'''馬恩島'''（{{lang-en|''Isle of Man''}}；{{lang-gv|Mannin}}，或''Ellan Vannin''），也被稱為'''曼恩'''（{{lang-en|''Mann''}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://manxnationalheritage.im/?s=mann|access-date=18 April 2022|title=Manx National Heritage}}</ref>，是一個[[島國|島國]]和自治的[[英國王室屬地|英國王室屬地]]，位於[[大不列顛島|大不列顛島]]和[[愛爾蘭島|愛爾蘭島]]之間的[[愛爾蘭海|愛爾蘭海]]。[[國家元首|國家元首]][[伊利沙伯二世|伊利沙伯二世女王]]，擁有[[馬恩島領主|馬恩島領主]]的頭銜並由一名{{tsl|en|Lieutenant Governor of the Isle of Man|副總督}}代表。[[英國|英國]]負責該島的軍事防禦。

自公元前6500年以來，一直就有人生活在島上。[[蓋爾人|蓋爾]]文化的影響始於公元5世紀，當時跟隨聖博德教導的愛爾蘭傳教士開始定居該島<ref>Britannica, T. Editors of Encyclopaedia. "Isle of Man." Encyclopedia Britannica, January 10, 2022. https://www.britannica.com/place/Isle-of-Man {{Wayback|url=https://www.britannica.com/place/Isle-of-Man |date=20220628042407 }}.</ref>，並且出現了[[蓋爾語|蓋爾語]]的一個分支[[馬恩島語|馬恩島語]]。在627年，諾森比亞國王{{tsl|en|Edwin of Northumbria|埃德溫}}征服了馬恩島連同[[麥西亞王國|麥西亞]]的大部分地區。9世紀，[[諾斯人|諾斯人]]建立了{{tsl|en|thalassocratic|海上霸權}}{{tsl|en|Kingdom of the Isles|群島王國}}，其中包括馬恩島。在1093年至1103年在位的的[[挪威|挪威]]國王[[馬格努斯三世|馬格努斯三世]]，曾在1099年至1103年之間作為{{tsl|en|King of Mann and the Isles|曼恩和群島國王}}統治<ref>{{cite web |date=28 September 2014 |title=Magnus 3 Olavsson Berrføtt – Norsk biografisk leksikon |url=https://nbl.snl.no/Magnus_3_Olavsson_Berrf%C3%B8tt |access-date=15 August 2019 |website=Store norske leksikon |language=no |archive-date=15 May 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515031012/http://snl.no/.nbl_biografi/Magnus_3_Olavsson_Berrf%C3%B8tt/utdypning |url-status=live }}</ref>。

在1266年，根據{{tsl|en|Treaty of Perth|珀斯條約}}，挪威國王[[馬格努斯六世|馬格努斯六世]]將他對曼恩的[[宗主權|宗主權]]賣給了蘇格蘭國王[[亞歷山大三世_(蘇格蘭)|亞歷山大三世]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.scottish-places.info/events/eventfirst171.html |title=Treaty of Perth: Overview of Treaty of Perth |publisher=Scottish-places.info |date= |accessdate=2022-02-26 |archive-date=2022-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220224122424/https://www.scottish-places.info/events/eventfirst171.html }}</ref>。在蘇格蘭和[[英格蘭王國|英格蘭]]國王交替統治一段時間後，該島於1399年落入[[英格蘭王國|英格蘭王室]]的封建領主之下。在1765年[[官方_(法人)|大不列顛王室]]{{tsl|en|Isle of Man Purchase Act 1765|重新}}獲得該主權，但該島並未成為18世紀的[[大不列顛王國|大不列顛王國]]及其繼承者[[大不列顛及愛爾蘭聯合王國|大不列顛及愛爾蘭聯合王國]]和今天[[大不列顛及北愛爾蘭聯合王國|大不列顛及北愛爾蘭聯合王國]]的一部分。它始終保持內部自治。在1881年，馬恩島[[議會|議會]][[馬恩島議會|廷瓦爾德]]成為世界上第一個賦予在大選中[[女性參政權|婦女投票權]]的國家[[立法機關|立法機關]]，儘管這將已婚婦女排除在外<ref>{{cite web |date=2017 |title=Tynwald, the parliament of the Isle of Man: Adult suffrage |url=http://www.tynwald.org.im/education/women/Pages/VotesForWomen.aspx |access-date=2 December 2017 |website=Tynwald.org.im |archive-date=26 April 2021 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210426153758/https://www.tynwald.org.im/education/women/Pages/VotesForWomen.aspx |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>在1893年，紐西蘭成為第一個給予''所有''女性投票權的國家。</ref>。

曼恩經濟因其避稅天堂和離岸銀行目的地的地位而得到支撐<ref>{{cite web |author=Matthew Collin |url=https://www.brookings.edu/blog/future-development/2021/05/05/the-hacker-the-tax-haven-and-what-200-million-in-offshore-deposits-can-tell-us-about-the-fight-against-illicit-wealth/ |title=The hacker, the tax haven, and what $200 million in offshore deposits can tell us about the fight against illicit wealth |publisher=Brookings.edu |date=2021-05-05 |accessdate=2022-03-15 |archive-date=2022-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220611080232/https://www.brookings.edu/blog/future-development/2021/05/05/the-hacker-the-tax-haven-and-what-200-million-in-offshore-deposits-can-tell-us-about-the-fight-against-illicit-wealth/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.britain-visitor.com/uk-city-guides/isle-of-man-guide |title=Isle of Man Guide | Britain Visitor - Travel Guide To Britain |publisher=Britain Visitor |date= |accessdate=2022-03-15 |archive-date=2022-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220610062007/https://www.britain-visitor.com/uk-city-guides/isle-of-man-guide }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/news/2017/nov/07/uk-isle-of-man-subsidy-tax-haven-common-purse-payments |title=UK is subsidising Isle of Man to be tax haven, say campaigners | Isle of Man |date=7 November 2017 |first=Juliette |last=Garside |newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |location=London |access-date=2022-03-15 |archive-date=2022-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220615023343/https://www.theguardian.com/news/2017/nov/07/uk-isle-of-man-subsidy-tax-haven-common-purse-payments }}</ref>。保險和[[在線賭博|在線賭博]]各佔[[國民生產總值|國民生產總值]]的17%，其次是[[信息及通信技術|信息及通信技術]]和銀行業，各佔9%<ref>{{cite web |title=Isle of Man: National Income Report |url=https://www.gov.im/media/1359185/national-income-2015-16-report-final.pdf |access-date=3 December 2017 |website=gov.im |archive-date=4 December 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171204062715/https://www.gov.im/media/1359185/national-income-2015-16-report-final.pdf |url-status=live }}</ref>。曼恩政府制定了一項戰略，需要採取“全島方法”來解決洗錢、金融犯罪和恐怖主義融資等嚴重問題。在國際上，馬恩島以[[曼島TT賽|TT]]電單車比賽<ref>{{Cite news |last=Williams |first=David |date=3 October 2017 |title=Great British drives: Isle of Man |language=en-GB |work=The Telegraph |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/destinations/europe/united-kingdom/england/isle-of-man/articles/great-british-drivesisleofman/ |access-date=15 August 2019 |issn=0307-1235 |quote=The Isle of Man is best known, of course, for its famous race, the annual Tourist Trophy, or 'TT'. |archive-date=9 February 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190209124520/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/destinations/europe/united-kingdom/england/isle-of-man/articles/great-british-drivesisleofman/ |url-status=live }}</ref>和[[曼島貓|曼島貓]]而聞名，曼島貓是一種短尾巴或沒有尾巴的品種<ref>{{Cite book |last=Long |first=Peter |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=4ePshlzYVkAC |title=The Hidden Places of England |publisher=Travel Publishing Ltd |year=1998 |isbn=9781904434122 |edition=4 |series=Hidden Places - National Guides |location=Aldermaston |publication-date=2004 |page=281 |chapter=Isle of Man |quote=Best known for its motorcycle races, its tailless cats and its kippers [...]. |access-date=9 March 2020 |archive-date=3 August 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803160644/https://books.google.com/books?id=4ePshlzYVkAC |url-status=live }}</ref> 。在2016年，[[聯合國教科文組織|聯合國教科文組織]]授予馬恩島[[世界生物圈保護區網絡|生物圈保護區地位]]<ref>{{cite web |title=UNESCO: Isle of Man biosphere reserve |url=http://www.unesco.org/new/en/natural-sciences/environment/ecological-sciences/biosphere-reserves/europe-north-america/united-kingdom-of-great-britain-and-northern-ireland/isle-of-man/ |access-date=2 December 2017 |archive-date=3 December 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171203224424/http://www.unesco.org/new/en/natural-sciences/environment/ecological-sciences/biosphere-reserves/europe-north-america/united-kingdom-of-great-britain-and-northern-ireland/isle-of-man/ |url-status=live }}</ref>。

