== 政府 ==
英國負責該島的防禦並最終負責{{tsl|en|Good governance|善政}}，並在國際場合上代表該島，而該島自己的議會和政府有權處理所有國內事務<ref>{{cite web |title=Isle of Man Government website |url=http://www.isleofmanfinance.gov.im/About/political.xml |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081014033149/http://www.isleofmanfinance.gov.im/About/political.xml |archive-date=14 October 2008 |access-date=10 November 2017 |website=Isleofmanfinance.gov.im}}</ref>。

=== 社會政治結構 ===
該島的議會[[馬恩島議會|廷瓦爾德]]據稱自979年或更早以來一直存在，據稱使其成為世界上最古老的連續管理機構，儘管證據支持的日期要晚得多<ref>{{cite web |title=Taking Liberties - Star Items - Chronicle of Mann |url=http://www.bl.uk/onlinegallery/takingliberties/staritems/322chronicleofmann.html |access-date=28 February 2015 |website=BL.uk |archive-date=24 September 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924035553/http://www.bl.uk/onlinegallery/takingliberties/staritems/322chronicleofmann.html |url-status=live }}</ref>。廷瓦爾德是一個{{tsl|en|Tricameralism|兩院制或三院制}}的立法機構，包括{{tsl|en|House of Keys|鑰匙院}}（由直接選舉的方式普選產生，最低投票年齡為16歲）和{{tsl|en|Legislative Council of the Isle of Man|馬恩島立法局|立法局}}（由間接選舉產生的議員和[[官守議員|官守議員]]組成）。這兩個機構還作為廷瓦爾德法院在聯合會議上開會。

政府的行政部門是{{tsl|en|Council of Ministers of the Isle of Man|部長理事會}}，由廷瓦爾德議員（通常是鑰匙院議員，儘管立法局議員也可能被任命為部長）組成。它由{{tsl|en|Chief Minister of the Isle of Man|馬恩島首席部長|首席部長}}領導。

國家元首的[[總督_(殖民地官職)|總督]]權由{{tsl|en|Lieutenant Governor of the Isle of Man|副總督}}行使。

=== 對外關係和安全 ===
在英國的各種法律中，“聯合王國”的定義不包括馬恩島。從歷史上看，英國一直處理其對外和國防事務，並保留為該島立法的至高無上的權力。然而在2007年，馬恩島和英國簽署了一項協議<ref name="framework">{{cite web |title=Framework for developing the international identity of the Isle of Man |url=http://www.gov.im/lib/docs/cso/iominternationalidentityframework.pdf |access-date=14 November 2018 |archive-date=20 April 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130420193544/http://www.gov.im/lib/docs/cso/iominternationalidentityframework.pdf |url-status=live }}</ref>，為發展馬恩島的國際身份建立了框架。沒有單獨的馬恩島公民身份。公民身份受英國法律保護，馬恩島人被歸類為英國公民。馬恩島和愛爾蘭之間有著悠久的關係和文化交流歷史。馬恩島歷史悠久的[[馬恩島語|馬恩島語]]（及其現代復興的變體）與蘇格蘭蓋爾語和愛爾蘭語密切相關，1947年，愛爾蘭總理[[埃蒙·德·瓦萊拉|埃蒙·德·瓦萊拉]]帶頭拯救垂死的馬恩島語<ref>[https://www.irishtimes.com/culture/one-small-step-for-man-1.99095 One small step for Man] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211029012347/https://www.irishtimes.com/country-cookie/ |date=29 October 2021 }}, ''[[Irish_Times|Irish Times]]'', 22 August 1997</ref>。

==== 防禦 ====
馬恩島不是英國的一部分，但是，英國負責其外交和國防事務<ref>{{Cite report |title=Royal Commission on the Constitution 1969–1973, Volume I, Report (Cmnd 5460) |date=1973 |location=London}}</ref>。馬恩島上沒有獨立的軍事力量，儘管{{tsl|en|HMS Ramsey (M110)|陛下之艦''拉姆齊號''}}起名於[[拉姆齊_(曼島)|同名城鎮]]<ref>{{cite web |date=2009 |title=HMS Ramsey |url=http://www.royalnavy.mod.uk/operations-and-support/surface-fleet/mine-countermeasure/sandown-class/hms-ramsey/ |access-date=11 September 2011 |publisher=Royal Navy |archive-date=30 August 2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100830150949/http://www.royalnavy.mod.uk/operations-and-support/surface-fleet/mine-countermeasure/sandown-class/hms-ramsey/ |url-status=live }}</ref>。從1938年到1955年，英國[[英國陸軍預備役部隊|領土軍隊]]的{{tsl|en|Manx Regiment|馬恩島團}}在[[第二次世界大戰|第二次世界大戰]]期間進行了廣泛的行動<ref>{{cite web |title=Regimental Museum – History |url=http://www.iomguide.com/douglas/regimental-museum.php |access-date=11 September 2011 |website=Isle of Man Guide |archive-date=3 November 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111103083203/http://www.iomguide.com/douglas/regimental-museum.php |url-status=live }}</ref>。在1779年，由三個連組成的{{tsl|en|Fencibles|防衛軍}}{{tsl|en|Royal Manx Fencibles|馬恩島防衛軍團}}成立；它於1783年在[[美國獨立戰爭|美國獨立戰爭]]結束時解散。後來，{{tsl|en|Royal Manx Fencibles|皇家馬恩島防衛軍}}在[[法國大革命戰爭|法國大革命戰爭]]和[[拿破崙戰爭|拿破崙戰爭]]時期成立。第一營（由三個連組成）於1793年成立。第二營（由十個連組成）於1795年成立<ref>See {{cite web |title=The Forgotten Army: Fencible Regiments of Great Britain 1793-1816 |url=http://www.napoleon-series.org/military/organization/fencibles/c_fencibles2.html |access-date=15 August 2019 |website=The Napoleon Series |archive-date=5 September 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120905025848/http://www.napoleon-series.org/military/organization/fencibles/c_fencibles2.html |url-status=live }} for more detail.</ref>，並在[[1798年愛爾蘭起義|1798年愛爾蘭起義]]期間採取了行動。該團於1802年解散<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Scobie |first=Ian Hamilton Mackay |year=1914 |title=An Old Highland Fencible Corps: The history of the Reay Fencible Highland Regiment of Foot, or Mackay's Highlanders, 1794–1802, with an account of its services in Ireland during the rebellion of 1798 |url=https://archive.org/stream/oldhighlandfenci00scobuoft#page/415/mode/1up |location=Edinburgh |publisher=Blackwood |page=363}}</ref>。在1803年，第三支馬恩島防衛軍成立，以在拿破崙戰爭期間保衛該島並協助收稅。它於1811年解散<ref>{{cite web |title=Regiments stationed on Isle of Man, 1765-1896 |url=http://www.isle-of-man.com/manxnotebook/history/military/regts.htm |access-date=28 February 2015 |website=Isle-of-man.com |archive-date=4 March 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304191403/http://www.isle-of-man.com/manxnotebook/history/military/regts.htm |url-status=live }}</ref>。{{tsl|en|Isle of Man Home Guard|馬恩島國民軍}}在[[第二次世界大戰|第二次世界大戰]]期間成立，用於本土防禦<ref>{{cite web |url=http://iomhomeguard.com/default.html |title=Isle of Man Home Guard Reenactment Society |access-date=28 January 2021 |archive-date=28 November 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128021410/http://iomhomeguard.com/default.html |url-status=live }}</ref>。在2015年，[[英國陸軍預備役部隊|英國陸軍預備役部隊]]的多功能招募和訓練單位在道格拉斯成立<ref name="Isle of Man Army Reserve">{{Cite news |date=October 2015 |title=British Army opens first reserve unit opens on Isle of Man since 1968 |work=BBC News |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-isle-of-man-34401508 |access-date=24 October 2016 |archive-date=25 October 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161025115619/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-isle-of-man-34401508 |url-status=live }}</ref>。

==== 馬恩島人地位 ====
[[File:Isle_of_man_passport.jpg|thumb]]

馬恩島沒有公民身份，因此馬恩島居民有權獲得英國公民身份，並可以獲得完整的聯合王國英國護照或英國馬恩島護照。

道格拉斯的馬恩島護照辦公室接受並處理提交給{{tsl|en|Lieutenant Governor of the Isle of Man|馬恩島副總督}}的護照申請，該副總督正式負責簽發由馬恩島簽發的名為“不列顛群島 - 馬恩島”的英國護照。1981年《英國國籍法》賦予英國内閣大臣的權力延伸至馬恩島，並由副總督在馬恩島行使<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gov.im/categories/travel-traffic-and-motoring/immigration/immigration-and-nationality-legislation |title=Isle of Man Government - Immigration and Nationality legislation |publisher=Gov.im |date= |accessdate=2022-03-15 |archive-date=2022-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220320002138/http://www.gov.im/categories/travel-traffic-and-motoring/immigration/immigration-and-nationality-legislation/ }}</ref>。

馬恩島簽發的英國護照目前可以發給居住在馬恩島的任何英國公民，也可以發給與馬恩島有合格的密切個人聯繫但現在居住在英國或英國的英國公民其他兩個王室屬地之一。

==== 歐洲聯盟 ====
馬恩島從來不是[[歐洲聯盟|歐洲聯盟]]的一部分，也沒有[[歐洲聯盟特別領域|特殊地位]]，因此沒有參加2016年英國作為[[歐盟|歐盟]]成員國身份去留問題的[[英國去留歐盟公投|公投]]<ref>[https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-eu-referendum-36618855 EU referendum: Brexit sends IoM on 'unknown journey] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200727005745/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-eu-referendum-36618855 |date=27 July 2020 }}, [[BBC_News|BBC News]], 24 June 2016</ref>然而，英國加入[[羅馬條約|羅馬條約]]法案的第3號議定書將馬恩島納入[[歐盟關稅同盟|歐盟關稅同盟]]，允許在整個歐盟範圍內進行馬恩島商品貿易而無需徵收關稅<ref>{{cite web |title=Manx government explanation of Protocol 3 |url=http://www.gov.im/lib/docs/ebusiness/advantages/protocol3.pdf |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080910004526/http://www.gov.im/lib/docs/ebusiness/advantages/protocol3.pdf |archive-date=10 September 2008 |access-date=10 November 2017 |website=Gov.im}}</ref>。由於它不是[[歐洲單一市場|歐洲單一市場]]的一部分，因此對資本、服務和勞動力的流動仍然存在限制。

歐盟公民有權在島上不受限制地旅行和居住，但不能工作。具有馬恩島人身份的英國公民與任何其他非歐盟歐洲相關國家在歐盟工作的情況和限制相同<ref>{{cite web |title=Isle of Man Facts & Economic Data |url=http://www.gov.im/categories/business-and-industries/iom-key-facts-guide/island-facts/ |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304050532/https://www.gov.im/categories/business-and-industries/iom-key-facts-guide/island-facts/ |archive-date=4 March 2016 |access-date=12 September 2010 |website=Isle of Man Finance |publisher=Isle of Man Government}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |date=October 2006 |title=Immigration in the Isle of Man |url=http://www.gov.im/lib/docs/cso/immigrationintheisleofmanpub.pdf |access-date=12 September 2010 |publisher=Isle of Man Government |page=12 |archive-date=11 May 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110511200914/http://www.gov.im/lib/docs/cso/immigrationintheisleofmanpub.pdf |url-status=live }}</ref>。

[[英國脫歐|英國脫歐]]對該島的政治和外交影響仍不確定。英國證實，英國皇家屬地的立場已包含在{{tsl|en|Brexit negotiations|英國脫歐談判}}中。<ref name="GRBWP">{{cite web |date=30 March 2017 |title=Legislating for the United Kingdom's withdrawal from the European Union |url=https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/604514/Great_repeal_bill_white_paper_print.pdf |publisher=Department for Exiting the European Union |access-date=16 May 2017 |archive-date=25 April 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170425050851/https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/604514/Great_repeal_bill_white_paper_print.pdf |url-status=live }}</ref>。[[英國脫歐協議|英國脫歐協議]]明確將馬恩島納入其領土範圍，但沒有其他提及<ref>{{cite web |date=14 November 2018 |title=Draft Agreement on the withdrawal of the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland from the European Union |url=https://ec.europa.eu/commission/sites/beta-political/files/draft_withdrawal_agreement_0.pdf |publisher=European Commission |access-date=19 July 2019 |archive-date=1 December 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201222743/https://ec.europa.eu/commission/sites/beta-political/files/draft_withdrawal_agreement_0.pdf |url-status=live }}</ref>。該島政府網站稱，在執行期結束後，馬恩島與歐盟的關係將取決於英國與歐盟就未來關係達成的協議<ref>{{cite web |title=Isle of Man Government - EU Exit and the Transition Period |url=https://www.gov.im/about-the-government/departments/cabinet-office/eu-exit-and-the-transition-period/ |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200620122427/https://www.gov.im/about-the-government/departments/cabinet-office/eu-exit-and-the-transition-period/ |archive-date=20 June 2020 |access-date=30 April 2020 |website=www.gov.im}}</ref>。

==== 英聯邦 ====
馬恩島不是[[英聯邦|英聯邦]]成員國。憑藉與英國的關係，它參加了多個英聯邦機構，包括{{tsl|en|Commonwealth Parliamentary Association|英聯邦議會協會}}和[[英聯邦運動會|英聯邦運動會]]。{{tsl|en|Council of Ministers of the Isle of Man|馬恩島政府}}呼籲與英聯邦建立更一體化的關係<ref>{{cite web |title=The role and future of the Commonwealth |url=https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201213/cmselect/cmfaff/114/11410.htm |access-date=18 March 2013 |publisher=House of Commons |archive-date=6 February 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130206123019/http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201213/cmselect/cmfaff/114/11410.htm |url-status=live }}</ref>，包括更直接的代表和更多地參與英聯邦組織和會議，包括英聯邦政府首腦會議<ref>{{cite web |title=Written evidence from the States of Guernsey |url=https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201213/cmselect/cmfaff/114/114we18.htm |access-date=18 March 2013 |publisher=Policy Council of Guernsey |archive-date=9 February 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130209074131/http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201213/cmselect/cmfaff/114/114we18.htm |url-status=live }}</ref>。{{tsl|en|Chief Minister of the Isle of Man|馬恩島首席部長}}曾說過：“與英聯邦本身建立更密切的聯繫將是該島國際關係的進一步發展<ref>{{Cite news |date=23 November 2012 |title=Isle of Man welcomes report on Commonwealth future |work=Isle of Man Government |url=http://www.gov.im/lib/news/cso/isleofmanwelcome5.xml |url-status=dead |access-date=19 March 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130302143313/http://www.gov.im/lib/news/cso/isleofmanwelcome5.xml |archive-date=2 March 2013}}</ref>。”

== 政治 ==
[[File:IsleOfMan_SheadingsAndParishes-en.svg|thumb]]

大多數馬恩島政治家以獨立人士而不是政黨代表的身份參選。儘管政黨確實存在，但它們的影響力遠不如英國那麼強大。

馬恩島有三個政黨：
* {{tsl|en|Liberal Vannin Party|自由曼恩黨}}（成立於2006年）在鑰匙院擁有一個席位；它促進了馬恩島更大的自治權和更多的政府問責制。
* {{tsl|en|Manx Labour Party|馬恩島工黨}}很活躍，在20世紀的大部分時間裡有幾個鑰匙院議員。目前（自2021年大選以來）鑰匙院有2名馬恩島工黨議員，她們都是女性。
* {{tsl|en|Isle of Man Green Party|馬恩島綠黨}}成立於2016年，但目前只有{{tsl|en|Local government in the Isle of Man|馬恩島地方政府|地方政府}}一級的代表<ref>{{Cite news |title=Isle of Man Green Party elects first councillor Andrew Bentley |work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-isle-of-man-45128963 |access-date=10 August 2018 |archive-date=30 March 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330183526/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-isle-of-man-45128963 |url-status=live }}</ref>。

島上還有許多壓力團體。{{tsl|en|Mec Vannin|馬恩島民族主義黨}}主張建立一個[[主權|主權]][[共和國|共和國]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Mec Vannin |url=http://www.mecvannin.im/ |access-date=28 February 2015 |website=Mecvannin.im |archive-date=9 February 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120209181627/http://www.mecvannin.im/psmenu.html |url-status=live }}</ref>。{{tsl|en|Positive Action Group|積極行動小組}}運動旨在將三個關鍵要素引入島嶼治理：公開負責的政府、嚴格控制公共財政和更公平的社會<ref>{{cite web |title=PAG - Positive Action Group - Isle of Man - Positive Action Group - Isle of Man - Pag, Credit, Agreement, User, February |url=http://www.positiveactiongroup.org/ |access-date=28 February 2015 |website=Positiveactiongroup.org |archive-date=21 March 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150321112422/http://www.positiveactiongroup.org/ |url-status=live }}</ref>。

=== 地方政府 ===
馬恩島的地方政府部分基於島上的17個古老教區。地方當局有四種類型：
* 道格拉斯自治市鎮的[[市法團|法團]]，以及[[卡斯爾敦_(曼島)|卡斯爾敦]]、[[皮爾_(曼島)|皮爾]]和[[拉姆齊_(曼島)|拉姆齊]]鎮區的專員機構
* {{tsl|en|Kirk Michael|米迦勒教堂}}和[[昂肯|昂肯]]區
* {{tsl|en|Port Erin|艾琳港}}和{{tsl|en|Port St Mary|聖瑪麗港 (曼島)|聖瑪麗港}}村區
* 13個教區（不屬於上述區域的歷史教區，或它們的組合或部分）。

這些地區中的每一個都有自己的專員機構。

==公共服務==
=== 教育 ===
公共教育隸屬於教育、體育和文化部。該部門下設三十二所小學、五所中學和{{tsl|en|University College Isle of Man|馬恩島大學學院}}<ref>{{cite web |date=21 November 2010 |title=Department of Education and Children Home Page |url=http://www.gov.im/education/ |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101121125241/http://www.gov.im/education/ |archive-date=21 November 2010 |access-date=15 August 2019 |website=Isle of Man Government Department of Education and Children}}</ref>。

=== 健康 ===
曼恩三分之二的居民超重或肥胖，十分之四的人缺乏運動，四分之一的人酗酒，十二分之一的人吸煙，大約15%的人總體健康狀況不佳<ref>{{Cite web |last=Butler |first=Nadia |last2=Quigg |first2=Zara |last3=Bates |first3=Rebecca |last4=Sayle |first4=Madeleine |last5=Ewart |first5=Henrietta |date=September 2021 |title=Isle of Man Health and Lifestyle Survey 2019 |url=https://www.gov.im/media/1374813/isle-of-man-health-and-lifestyle-survey-2019_compressed-031221.pdf |publisher=Liverpool John Moores University |access-date=2022-04-06 |archive-date=2022-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220402090910/https://www.gov.im/media/1374813/isle-of-man-health-and-lifestyle-survey-2019_compressed-031221.pdf }}</ref>。醫療保健是通過{{tsl|en|Department of Health and Social Care (Isle of Man)|衛生和社會保健部}}的一項公共衛生計劃為來自英國的居民和遊客提供的<ref>{{cite web |title=Healthcare on the Isle of Man |url=https://www.locate.im/article/practical-advice/healthcare-on-the-isle-of-man/ |access-date=4 October 2017 |website=LOcate IM |archive-date=4 October 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171004140530/https://www.locate.im/article/practical-advice/healthcare-on-the-isle-of-man/ |url-status=live }}</ref>。

=== 犯罪 ===
曼恩的犯罪嚴重率主要衡量針對人員或財產的犯罪，儘管近年來暴力犯罪率一直在上升，但仍大大低於英國其他地區。大多數暴力犯罪與非法毒品交易有關<ref>{{Cite web |title=CHIEF CONSTABLE’S ANNUAL REPORT 2019-2020 |url=https://www.tynwald.org.im/business/opqp/sittings/20182021/2020-GD-0020.pdf |website=Tynwald - Parliament of the Isle of Man |access-date=2022-04-06 |archive-date=2022-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220501094832/https://www.tynwald.org.im/business/opqp/sittings/20182021/2020-GD-0020.pdf }}</ref>。

曼恩政府制定了一項戰略，需要採取“全島辦法”來解決洗錢、金融犯罪和恐怖主義融資等嚴重問題<ref>{{Cite web |date=June 2021 |title=Financial Crime Strategy 2021-23 |url=https://www.gov.im/media/1373450/isle-of-man-financial-crime-strategy-2021-2023.pdf |website=Isle of Man Cabinet Office |access-date=2022-04-06 |archive-date=2021-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210709100614/https://www.gov.im/media/1373450/isle-of-man-financial-crime-strategy-2021-2023.pdf }}</ref>。

=== 緊急服務 ===
馬恩島政府維持五個緊急服務<ref>{{cite web |date=16 August 2013 |title=Emergency services |url=http://cf.gov.im/categories/home-and-neighbourhood/emergency-services/ |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130816235226/http://cf.gov.im/categories/home-and-neighbourhood/emergency-services/ |archive-date=16 August 2013 |access-date=15 August 2019 |website=Isle of Man Government}}</ref>。這些是：
* {{tsl|en|Isle of Man Constabulary|馬恩島警察}}（警察）
* {{tsl|en|Isle of Man Coastguard|馬恩島海岸警衛隊}}
* {{tsl|en|Isle of Man Fire and Rescue Service|馬恩島消防和救援服務}}
* {{tsl|en|Isle of Man Ambulance Service|馬恩島救護車服務}}
* {{tsl|en|Isle of Man Civil Defence Corps|馬恩島民防隊}}

所有這些服務均由馬恩島政府{{tsl|en|Department of Home Affairs (Isle of Man)|馬恩島內政部|內政部}}直接控制，獨立於英國。儘管如此，馬恩島警察自願接受英國警察檢查局的檢查<ref>{{cite web |title=Welcome to the Isle of Man Constabulary |url=http://www.gov.im/dha/police/ |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070303101639/http://www.gov.im/dha/police/ |archive-date=3 March 2007 |access-date=11 September 2011 |publisher=Isle of Man Government}}</ref>，並且馬恩島海岸警衛隊與女王陛下海岸警衛隊（英國）簽訂了海空救援行動的合同。

=== 火葬場 ===
島上唯一的火葬場位於道格拉斯的格倫克魯奇路，由道格拉斯自治市鎮委員會運營。通常有4名工作人員，2020年3月，理事會領導人宣布將工作人員增加到12人，以應對可能需要更多工作人員的[[武漢肺炎|武漢肺炎]]威脅<ref>{{Cite news |date=13 March 2020 |title=More staff trained to operate island's crematorium |language=en-GB |work=BBC News |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-isle-of-man-51861337 |access-date=30 April 2020 |archive-date=13 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200313085437/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-isle-of-man-51861337 |url-status=live }}</ref>。

== 經濟 ==
馬恩島沒有[[資本利得稅|資本利得稅]]、[[財富稅|財富稅]]、[[印花稅|印花稅]]或[[遺產稅|遺產稅]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Financial Services Sector - Isle of Man. Where You Can. |url=http://www.gov.im/iomfinance/tax/directtax.xml |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120419122502/http://www.gov.im/iomfinance/tax/directtax.xml |archive-date=19 April 2012 |access-date=28 February 2015 |website=Gov.im |publisher=IsleofMan Government}}</ref>，[[所得稅|所得稅]]最高稅率為20%<ref name="opw">{{cite web |date=2017 |title=Isle of Man Government: Rates & Allowances 2017/2018 |url=https://www.gov.im/categories/tax-vat-and-your-money/income-tax-and-national-insurance/individuals/residents/rates-and-allowances/ |access-date=2 December 2017 |website=Gov.im |publisher=Isle of Man Government |archive-date=26 June 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180626220519/https://www.gov.im/categories/tax-vat-and-your-money/income-tax-and-national-insurance/individuals/residents/rates-and-allowances/ |url-status=live }}</ref>。稅收上限生效：如果夫妻選擇共同評估其收入，則個人應繳納的最高稅額為200,000英鎊或400,000英鎊。個人收入按全球總收入而非[[僑匯|僑匯]]基礎進行評估和徵稅。這意味著在世界各地賺取的所有收入都應繳納馬恩島稅，而不僅僅是在島上賺取或帶入該島的收入。[[公司稅|公司稅]]的標準稅率居民和非居民為0%。超過500,000英鎊的零售業務利潤和銀行業務收入按10%徵稅，馬恩島土地和建築物的租金（或其他）收入按20%徵稅<ref>{{cite web |title=Isle of Man Government: Corporate Tax Rules |url=https://www.gov.im/categories/tax-vat-and-your-money/income-tax-and-national-insurance/business-and-corporations/corporate-tax-rates/ |access-date=2 December 2017 |website=Gov.im |archive-date=29 November 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171129171851/https://www.gov.im/categories/tax-vat-and-your-money/income-tax-and-national-insurance/business-and-corporations/corporate-tax-rates/ |url-status=live }}</ref>。
[[File:Peel_-_Peel_Bay_Beach_-_geograph.org.uk_-_1719663.jpg|thumb]]是島上的主要漁港。]]

曼恩的低公司稅負擔<ref>{{cite web |url=https://taxfoundation.org/publications/corporate-tax-rates-around-the-world/ |title=Corporate Tax Rates Around the World |publisher=Tax Foundation |date=2021-12-09 |accessdate=2022-03-15 |archive-date=2022-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220628013745/https://taxfoundation.org/publications/corporate-tax-rates-around-the-world/ }}</ref> 和缺乏公司所有權的公共登記<ref>{{cite web |url=https://cpa.co.uk/jersey-guernsey-and-the-isle-of-man-to-reveal-who-owns-offshore-firms/ |title=Jersey, Guernsey and the Isle of Man to reveal who owns offshore firms - CPA | The Credit Protection Association |publisher=CPA |date=2019-06-21 |accessdate=2022-03-15 |archive-date=2022-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220617035746/https://cpa.co.uk/jersey-guernsey-and-the-isle-of-man-to-reveal-who-owns-offshore-firms/ }}</ref>為個人和公司提供了[[避稅|避稅]]和[[逃稅|逃稅]]策略，導致大量資金從追求稅收優勢和財務保密的人那裡湧入<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.elibrary.imf.org/view/books/071/29292-9781513575919-en/ch003.xml |title=Chapter 2 Europe's Shadow Economies: Estimating Size and Outlining Policy Options in: The Global Informal Workforce |publisher=Elibrary.imf.org |date=2021-07-23 |accessdate=2022-02-26 |archive-date=2022-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220224190148/https://www.elibrary.imf.org/view/books/071/29292-9781513575919-en/ch003.xml }}</ref>。作為馬恩島經濟的前支柱，農業、漁業和旅遊業的相對重要性相應下降<ref name="theconversation1">{{cite web |author=Pete Hodson |url=https://theconversation.com/the-isle-of-man-is-a-tax-haven-but-its-prosperity-has-precarious-roots-87146 |title=The Isle of Man is a tax haven – but its prosperity has precarious roots |publisher=Theconversation.com |date=2017-11-09 |accessdate=2022-02-26 |archive-date=2022-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220501094835/https://theconversation.com/the-isle-of-man-is-a-tax-haven-but-its-prosperity-has-precarious-roots-87146 }}</ref>。作為典型的低稅王室屬地，曼恩的經濟以金融服務、高科技公司的空殼公司、在線賭博和在線遊戲為特色<ref>{{cite web |author=Gambling Supervision Commission |url=https://www.gov.im/categories/business-and-industries/gambling-and-e-gaming/ |title=Isle of Man Government - Gambling and e-gaming |publisher=Gov.im |date=2021-01-19 |accessdate=2022-02-26 |archive-date=2022-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220620205512/https://www.gov.im/categories/business-and-industries/gambling-and-e-gaming/ }}</ref>，電影製作和高淨值人士的避稅天堂<ref>{{cite web|author=Ryan Chittum, Tim Robinson, and Juliette Garside |url=https://www.irishtimes.com/business/paradise-papers-a-two-hour-stop-in-the-isle-of-man-can-save-you-millions-in-tax-on-a-private-jet-1.3281663 |title=Paradise Papers: A two-hour stop in the Isle of Man can save you millions in tax on a private jet |publisher=Irishtimes.com |date=2017-11-06 |accessdate=2022-02-26}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/news/2017/nov/06/isle-of-man-refunds-super-rich-private-jets-paradise-papers |title=How Isle of Man gives big refunds to super-rich on private jet imports | Isle of Man |work=The Guardian |date= |accessdate=2022-02-26 |archive-date=2022-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220611135115/https://www.theguardian.com/news/2017/nov/06/isle-of-man-refunds-super-rich-private-jets-paradise-papers }}</ref>。這些活動為曼恩帶來了一些高收入工作，因為數百名當地居民擔任“稻草人”董事和空殼公司股東<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Jancsics |first1=David |title=Shell Companies and Government Corruption |journal=Global Encyclopedia of Public Administration, Public Policy, and Governance |date=2018 |pages=1–5 |doi=10.1007/978-3-319-31816-5_3566-1|isbn=978-3-319-31816-5 }}</ref>。類似的計劃為高淨值個人提供了一種手段減少他們的稅收義務並保護他們的金融交易免受公眾審查<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.icij.org/investigations/paradise-papers/elite-touch-down-on-isle-of-man-to-avoid-millions-in-tax/|title=Elite touch down on Isle of Man to avoid millions in tax - ICIJ|date=25 August 2020|access-date=2022-04-17|archive-date=2022-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220609224455/https://www.icij.org/investigations/paradise-papers/elite-touch-down-on-isle-of-man-to-avoid-millions-in-tax/}}</ref><ref name="theconversation1"/>。如[[天堂文件|天堂文件]]所述<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/news/series/paradise-papers |title=Paradise Papers: A special investigation | Paradise-papers |work=The Guardian |date= |accessdate=2022-02-26 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225143807/https://www.theguardian.com/news/series/paradise-papers }}</ref>，馬恩島經濟具有廣泛的非法經濟活動，包括逃稅、從毒品銷售中洗錢、來自武器銷售的資金轉移，以及掠奪其他民族國家（尤其是俄羅斯）的公共國庫<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/news/2017/nov/14/after-successive-offshore-scandals-are-there-signs-of-change-in-isle-of-man |title=After successive offshore scandals, are there signs of change in Isle of Man? | Paradise Papers |work=The Guardian |date= |accessdate=2022-02-26 |archive-date=2022-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220628141344/https://www.theguardian.com/news/2017/nov/14/after-successive-offshore-scandals-are-there-signs-of-change-in-isle-of-man }}</ref>這些資金主要流入倫敦金融市場。儘管馬恩島政府採取的法律措施的影響仍不確定，但一直在努力規範這些活動<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-isle-of-man-59595491 |title=Isle of Man launches strategy to tackle bribery and corruption - BBC News |publisher=Bbc.com |date= |accessdate=2022-02-26 |archive-date=2022-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220617175148/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-isle-of-man-59595491 }}</ref>。在線賭博網站在2014年提供了大約10%的島嶼收入。馬恩島目前可以自由進入歐盟市場，並且主要與英國進行貿易。馬恩島與歐盟的貿易關係源於英國的歐盟成員身份，鑑於英國決定退出歐盟，需要重新談判。預計過渡期將允許貨物和農產品自由流動到歐盟，直到2020年底或談判達成新的解決方案。

馬恩島{{tsl|en|Department for Enterprise (Isle of Man)|馬恩島企業部|企業部}}管理12個關鍵部門的多元化經濟<ref>{{cite web |title=Isle of Man: Key sectors |url=http://www.whereyoucan.com/sectors |access-date=2 December 2017 |archive-date=3 December 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171203153908/http://www.whereyoucan.com/sectors |url-status=live }}</ref>。GNP最大的部門是保險和[[網絡賭博|網絡賭博]]，各佔GNP的17%，其次是[[資訊及通訊科技|ICT]]和銀行業，各佔9%。2016年人口普查列出了41,636名僱員<ref name="census-2016">{{cite web |title=2016 Isle of Man Census Report |url=https://www.gov.im/news/2022/feb/02/first-details-of-2021-census-report-published/ |access-date=2 February 2022 |website=gov.im |archive-date=2022-05-01 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220501095106/https://www.gov.im/news/2022/feb/02/first-details-of-2021-census-report-published/ }}</ref>。就業人數最多的部門是“醫療和健康”、“金融和商業服務”、建築、零售和公共管理<ref>{{cite web |title=2016 Isle of Man Census Presentation |url=https://www.gov.im/media/1355783/2016-isle-of-man-census-presentation.pdf |access-date=2 December 2017 |archive-date=3 December 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171203013850/https://www.gov.im/media/1355783/2016-isle-of-man-census-presentation.pdf |url-status=live }}</ref>。製造業，專注於航空航天和食品和飲料行業<ref>{{cite web |title=Isle of Man Manufacturing Sector |url=http://www.whereyoucan.com/manufacturing |access-date=2 December 2017 |website=whereyoucan.im (Department for Enterprise) |archive-date=3 December 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171203153911/http://www.whereyoucan.com/manufacturing |url-status=live }}</ref>，僱傭了近2000名工人，約佔[[國內生產總值|國內生產總值]]（GDP）的5%。該部門提供激光光學、工業鑽石、電子、塑料和航空航天精密工程。旅遊業、農業和漁業曾經是經濟的支柱，現在對該島的GDP貢獻微乎其微。馬恩島的失業率低於1%<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.gov.im/news/2022/mar/15/labour-market-report-for-february-2022/|title=Isle of Man Government - Labour market report for February 2022|website=www.gov.im|access-date=2022-04-17|archive-date=2022-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220501094828/https://www.gov.im/news/2022/mar/15/labour-market-report-for-february-2022/}}</ref>。

貿易主要發生在英國。該島與英國是關稅同盟，相關收入根據{{tsl|en|Common Purse Agreement|共同錢包協議}}匯集和分享。這意味著馬恩島不能享受[[海峽群島|海峽群島]]所享有的酒類和其他商品的較低消費稅收入。

馬恩島政府通過提供財政支持{{tsl|en|Isle of Man Film|來促進島嶼拍攝電影}}。自1995年以來，已在島上製作了100多部電影。<ref>{{cite web |date=27 September 2013 |title=Isle of Man Film |url=https://www.isleofmanfilm.com/about/ |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171204061234/https://www.isleofmanfilm.com/about/ |archive-date=4 December 2017 |access-date=3 December 2017}}</ref>最近，該島採取了更廣泛的戰略，以吸引電影、電視、影片和[[電子競技|電子競技]]領域的一般數字媒體行業<ref>{{cite web |title=Isle of Man Digital Media Cluster. Strategic Directions for the Isle of Man |url=http://isleofmedia.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Isle-of-Media-National-Strategy.pdf |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222064658/http://isleofmedia.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Isle-of-Media-National-Strategy.pdf |archive-date=22 December 2017 |access-date=3 December 2017}}</ref>。

馬恩島政府彩票於1986年至1997年運營。自1999年12月2日起，該島參加了[[國家彩票|英國國家彩票]]<ref>{{cite web |title=ontheisleofman.com |url=http://www.ontheisleofman.com/can-i-play-the-national-lottery-on-the-isle-of-man/ |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170630005340/http://www.ontheisleofman.com/can-i-play-the-national-lottery-on-the-isle-of-man/ |archive-date=30 June 2017 |access-date=10 November 2017 |website=Ontheisleofman.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=UK National Lottery Diary |url=http://lottery.merseyworld.com/Info/Diary.html |access-date=28 February 2015 |website=Merseyworld.com |archive-date=19 March 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150319210353/http://lottery.merseyworld.com/Info/Diary.html |url-status=live }}</ref>。該島是英國以外唯一可以玩英國國家彩票的司法管轄區<ref>{{cite web |title=National Lottery FAQ:Can I play while overseas? |url=http://www.national-lottery.co.uk/player/p/help/faqs.ftl#int_GetStarted2 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140703194651/https://www.national-lottery.co.uk/player/p/help/faqs.ftl#int_GetStarted2 |archive-date=3 July 2014 |access-date=10 November 2017 |website=National-lottery.co.uk}}</ref>。自2010年以來，馬恩島的項目也有可能獲得國家彩票{{tsl|en|The National Lottery Awards|善因基金}}<ref>{{Cite news |date=20 June 2010 |title=BBC News - Manx charities to benefit from lottery |work=BBC News |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/10361512 |access-date=28 February 2015 |archive-date=22 September 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140922095859/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/10361512 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=House of Lords - Constitution - Ninth Report |url=https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/ld200506/ldselect/ldconst/151/15107.htm |access-date=28 February 2015 |website=Parliament.uk |archive-date=18 February 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150218051045/http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/ld200506/ldselect/ldconst/151/15107.htm |url-status=live }}</ref>善因資金由馬恩島彩票信托分配<ref>{{cite web |title=About |url=http://www.mlt.org.im/ |access-date=28 February 2015 |website=MLT.org.im |publisher=Manx Lottery Trust |archive-date=2 March 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150302163433/http://www.mlt.org.im/ |url-status=live }}</ref>。[[馬恩島議會|廷瓦爾德]]收到在島上出售的門票12%的彩票稅。

旅遊人數在20世紀上半葉達到頂峰，在此之前，南歐廉價旅遊的繁榮也見證了許多類似的英國海濱度假勝地的旅遊業下滑。馬恩島旅遊局最近投資了“暗天探索”網站，以使其旅遊業多樣化。預計黑暗的天空通常將由英國各地的公眾提名。然而，馬恩島旅遊局委託他們團隊中的某個人提名島上的27個地方作為民事任務。這個最高質量的“銀河”網站集群<ref>{{cite web |title=Dark Sky Discovery Sites |url=http://www.darkskydiscovery.org.uk/dark-sky-discovery-sites/map.html#sites |access-date=10 November 2017 |website=Darkskydiscovery.org.uk |archive-date=10 November 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171110012420/http://www.darkskydiscovery.org.uk/dark-sky-discovery-sites/map.html#sites |url-status=live }}</ref>現在在島內得到很好的推廣。政府的這一推動有效地使該島在公認的黑暗天空遺址數量上領先一步。然而，與未在全國范圍內推廣的英國相比，這造成了一種扭曲的觀點。在那裡，隨著時間的推移，預計黑暗天空站點將在整個城鎮、城市和農村地區由公眾提名，而不是由政府部門''集體提名''<ref>{{cite web |title=Stargazing Sites in the Isle of Man - Isle of Man |url=http://www.visitisleofman.com/placestovisit/darkskysites/darkskies.xml |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160911125709/http://www.visitisleofman.com/placestovisit/darkskysites/darkskies.xml |archive-date=11 September 2016 |access-date=10 November 2017 |website=Visitisleofman.com}}</ref>。

2017年，{{tsl|en|The International Stock Exchange|國際證券交易所}}辦事處成立，以促進島上的金融業<ref>{{cite web |date=9 March 2017 |title=Carolyn Gelling to lead new stock exchange company |url=http://www.iomtoday.co.im/article.cfm?id=32400&headline=Carolyn%20Gelling%20to%20lead%20new%20stock%20exchange%20company&sectionIs=news&searchyear=2017 |website=IOMToday |access-date=11 March 2017 |archive-date=12 March 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312044209/http://www.iomtoday.co.im/article.cfm?id=32400&headline=Carolyn%20Gelling%20to%20lead%20new%20stock%20exchange%20company&sectionIs=news&searchyear=2017 |url-status=live }}</ref>。

=== 通訊 ===
[[File:cmglee_Douglas_Isle_of_Man_aerial_view.jpg|thumb]]
馬恩島的主要電話提供商是{{tsl|en|Manx Telecom|馬恩島電訊}}。該島有兩家移動運營商：馬恩島電訊（以前稱為Manx Pronto）和{{tsl|en|Sure (company)|Sure}}。{{tsl|en|Cloud9 (service provider)|Cloud9 (服務提供商)|Cloud9}}作為島上的第三家移動運營商運營了很短的時間，但後來退出了。

寬帶互聯網服務可通過四家本地提供商獲得：Wi-Manx、Domicilium、Manx Computer Bureau和{{tsl|en|Manx Telecom|馬恩島電訊}}。該島沒有自己的[[國際電聯|國際電聯]][[國際電話區號列表|國家代碼]]，但可通過英國國家代碼（+44）訪問，該島的電話號碼是{{tsl|en|Telephone numbers in the United Kingdom|英國電話號碼計劃}}的一部分，本地撥號代碼01624用於固定電話，07524、07624和07924用於手機。但是，從英國撥打該島的電話通常與英國境內的收費不同，並且可能包含或可能不包含在任何“包含分鐘”套餐中<ref>{{cite web |title=Phone Tariff Residential |url=http://www.productsandservices.bt.com/consumer/assets/downloads/BT_PhoneTariff_Residential.pdf |website=BT.com |publisher=[[BT_Group|BT Group]] |access-date=30 May 2017 |archive-date=14 September 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150914151455/http://www.productsandservices.bt.com/consumer/assets/downloads/BT_PhoneTariff_Residential.pdf |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Calling abroad from the UK |url=http://international.o2.co.uk/internationaltariffs/calling_abroad_from_uk |website=O2.com |publisher=Telefónica Europe |access-date=30 May 2017 |archive-date=25 May 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170525225346/http://international.o2.co.uk/internationaltariffs/calling_abroad_from_uk |url-status=live }}</ref>。

1996年，馬恩島政府獲得使用[[.im|.im]]作為國家[[頂級域名|頂級域名]]（TLD）的許可，並對其使用負最終責任。主要由位於島嶼的互聯網服務提供商Domicilium日常管理。2007年12月，{{tsl|en|Manx Electricity Authority|馬恩島電力局}}及其電信子公司e-llan Communications委託鋪設一條新的光纖鏈路，將該島連接到全球光纖網絡。據報導，2021年8月，美國企業家[[埃隆·馬斯克|埃隆·馬斯克]]創辦的衛星互聯網服務[[星鏈|星鏈]]已獲得在島上一個地面站運營的許可證。

馬恩島有三個廣播電台：{{tsl|en|Manx Radio|馬恩島電台}}、{{tsl|en|Energy FM (Isle of Man)|Energy FM}}和3FM。

沒有孤立的電視服務，但本地發射器通過免費[[地面數碼電視|地面數碼電視]]服務[[Freeview|Freeview]]轉播英國大陸數碼廣播。馬恩島由[[BBC西北|BBC西北]]為[[BBC_One|BBC One]]和[[BBC_Two|BBC Two]]提供電視服務，[[ITV格拉納達|ITV格拉納達]]為[[獨立電視網|獨立電視網]]提供服務。

許多電視服務都可以通過衛星獲得，例如來自{{tsl|en|Astra 28.2°E|阿斯特拉東經28.2°}}的衛星組的[[天空英國|天空英國]]和{{tsl|en|Freesat|Freesat}}，以及來自歐洲其他一系列衛星的服務，例如{{tsl|en|Astra 19.2°E|阿斯特拉東經19.2°}}的{{tsl|en|SES Astra|SES阿斯特拉|阿斯特拉}}衛星和{{tsl|en|Hot Bird|Hot Bird}}。

馬恩島擁有三份報紙，均為周刊，均由愛丁堡媒體公司{{tsl|en|Johnston Press|約翰斯頓出版社}}旗下的{{tsl|en|Isle of Man Newspapers|馬恩島報紙}}擁有<ref>{{cite web |title=Our Business |url=http://www.johnstonpress.co.uk/jpplc/ourbusiness/publishingdivision/division.jsp |access-date=12 September 2011 |publisher=Johnston Press}}{{dead link|date=March 2020|bot=medic}}{{cbignore|bot=medic}}</ref>。{{tsl|en|Isle of Man Courier|馬恩島信使}}（分發量36,318份）是免費的，分發給島上的家庭。另外兩家報紙是{{tsl|en|Isle of Man Examiner|馬恩島審查員}}（發行量13,276份）和{{tsl|en|Manx Independent|馬恩島獨立報}}（發行量12,255份）<ref>{{cite web |title=Isle of Man Newspapers |url=http://www.iomtoday.co.im/newspaper.aspx |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080822194758/http://www.iomtoday.co.im/newspaper.aspx |archive-date=22 August 2008 |access-date=4 September 2008 |website=IOMToday |publisher=[[Isle_of_Man_Newspapers|Isle of Man Newspapers]]}}</ref>。

郵政服務由{{tsl|en|Isle of Man Post Office|馬恩島郵局}}負責，該郵局於1973年從英國的{{tsl|en|General Post Office|英國郵政總局|郵政總局}}接管。

=== 運輸 ===
[[File:Douglas_Sea_Terminal_-_Isle_of_Man_-_kingsley_-_20-APR-09.jpg|thumb]]
有一個全面的巴士網絡，由國有巴士運營商{{tsl|en|Bus Vannin|馬恩島巴士}}運營<ref>{{cite web |title=Isle of Man Government - Bus and Rail |url=https://www.gov.im/categories/travel-traffic-and-motoring/bus-and-rail/ |access-date=12 November 2017 |website=Gov.im |archive-date=10 November 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171110151806/https://www.gov.im/categories/travel-traffic-and-motoring/bus-and-rail/ |url-status=live }}</ref>。

道格拉斯的{{tsl|en|Isle of Man Sea Terminal|馬恩島海運碼頭}}有往返[[希舍姆|希舍姆]]和[[利物浦|利物浦]]的定期渡輪，冬季運營的時間表更受限制。這兩艘船是''Manannan''和''Ben My Chree''。後者將於2022年被[[現代重工|現代重工]]製造的新船取代；它於2020年年中被公眾命名為''馬恩島人''。往返[[貝爾法斯特|貝爾法斯特]]和[[都柏林|都柏林]]的夏季服務也有限。都柏林路線也在聖誕節運營。在[[曼島TT賽|曼島TT賽]]時期，往返[[北愛爾蘭|北愛爾蘭]]{{tsl|en|Larne Harbour railway station|拉恩港火車站|拉恩}}的航行數量有限。所有渡輪均由{{tsl|en|Isle of Man Steam Packet Company|馬恩島蒸汽郵船公司}}運營<ref>{{cite web |title=Steam Packet Company |url=https://www.steam-packet.com/?__SPCoWinID=fb3a8cbb-61ce-40aa-bf27-95e1d8d2e301 |access-date=10 November 2017 |website=Steam-packet.com |archive-date=15 October 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015203048/https://www.steam-packet.com/?__SPCoWinID=fb3a8cbb-61ce-40aa-bf27-95e1d8d2e301 |url-status=live }}</ref>。

島上唯一的商業機場是{{tsl|en|Ronaldsway|朗奴士威}}的{{tsl|en|Isle of Man Airport|馬恩島機場}}。有直飛英國和愛爾蘭眾多機場的定期和包機航班<ref>{{cite web |title=Isle of Man Government - Isle of Man Airport |url=https://www.gov.im/categories/travel-traffic-and-motoring/isle-of-man-airport/ |access-date=10 November 2017 |website=Gov.im |archive-date=15 October 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015202056/https://www.gov.im/categories/travel-traffic-and-motoring/isle-of-man-airport/ |url-status=live }}</ref>。

島上共有{{convert|688|mi}}<ref>{{cite web |title=Isle of Man – About the Island |url=http://www.isleofman.com/tourism/about/ |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080225093426/http://www.isleofman.com/tourism/about |archive-date=25 February 2008 |access-date=10 November 2017 |website=Isleofman.com}}</ref>的公共道路，全部鋪設。沒有壓倒一切的國家速度限制；只設置了當地的限速，有些道路沒有限速。關於魯莽駕駛的規則和大多數其他駕駛法規的執行方式與英國類似<ref name="speed01">{{cite web |date=2005 |title=Driving on the Isle of Man |url=http://www.iomguide.com/drivingontheisleofman.php |access-date=8 June 2010 |website=Isle of Man Guide |publisher=Maxima Systems |archive-date=18 November 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181118164713/http://www.iomguide.com/drivingontheisleofman.php |url-status=live }}</ref> 。某些車輛需要定期進行車輛檢查（類似於英國的交通運輸部測試）<ref>{{cite web |date=1 January 1988 |title=Vehicle examination |url=https://www.gov.im/categories/travel-traffic-and-motoring/drivers-and-vehicles/vehicle-registration-and-licensing/vehicle-examination/ |access-date=15 August 2019 |website=Isle of Man Government |archive-date=19 December 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181219230208/https://www.gov.im/categories/travel-traffic-and-motoring/drivers-and-vehicles/vehicle-registration-and-licensing/vehicle-examination/ |url-status=live }}</ref>。

該島曾經擁有廣泛的{{tsl|en|British narrow-gauge railways|英國窄軌鐵路|窄軌鐵路}}系統，既有蒸汽驅動的也有電動的，但大部分蒸汽鐵路軌道在多年前就停止服務，軌道被拆除。截至2022年，道格拉斯和艾琳港之間有一條[[曼島鐵路|蒸汽鐵路]]，道格拉斯和拉姆齊之間有一條{{tsl|en|Manx Electric Railway|馬恩島電氣鐵路|電氣化鐵路}}，還有一條攀登{{tsl|en|Snaefell|斯奈菲爾山}}的{{tsl|en|Snaefell Mountain Railway|斯奈菲爾山鐵路|電氣化山區鐵路}}<ref name="Heritage" />。

最古老的馬車服務之一位於首都[[道格拉斯_(曼島)|道格拉斯]]的海濱。它成立於1876年<ref name="Heritage">{{cite web |date=2017 |title=Heritage Railways |url=https://www.gov.im/categories/travel-traffic-and-motoring/bus-and-rail/heritage-railways/ |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190315110306/https://www.gov.im/categories/travel-traffic-and-motoring/bus-and-rail/heritage-railways/ |archive-date=15 March 2019 |access-date=8 November 2017 |website=Gov.im |publisher=Isle of Man Government}}</ref>。

=== 太空商業 ===
馬恩島已成為新興{{tsl|en|Private spaceflight|私人太空旅行}}公司的中心<ref>{{cite web |last=Goodman |first=Mike |date=22 July 2011 |title=Lift-off for Isle of Man's quest to join space race |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/personalfinance/offshorefinance/8644850/Lift-off-for-Isle-of-Mans-quest-to-join-space-race.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110724020838/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/personalfinance/offshorefinance/8644850/Lift-off-for-Isle-of-Mans-quest-to-join-space-race.html |url-status=dead |archive-date=24 July 2011 |access-date=12 September 2011 |website=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]}}</ref>。[[Google月球X大獎|Google月球X大獎]]（一項3000萬美元的第一個將機器人送上月球的私人資助團隊的比賽）的許多參賽者都以該島為基地。X大獎團隊峰會於2010年10月在島上舉行<ref>{{cite web |date=18 October 2010 |title=Lunar Entrepreneurs Converge on Isle of Man for Google Lunar X PRIZE Summit |url=http://www.googlelunarxprize.com/media-center/press-release/lunar-entrepreneurs-converge-on-isle-of-man-for-google-lunar-x-prize-summ |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120402103131/http://www.googlelunarxprize.com/media-center/press-release/lunar-entrepreneurs-converge-on-isle-of-man-for-google-lunar-x-prize-summ |archive-date=2 April 2012 |access-date=12 September 2011 |website=GoogleLunarXPrize.com}}</ref>。2011年1月，[[王劍鑽石|王劍鑽石]]擁有的兩個研究空間站抵達島上，並被存放在{{tsl|en|Jurby|朱比 (曼島)|朱比}}附近前{{tsl|en|Private spaceflight|朱比皇家空軍基地}}的機場飛機庫中<ref>{{cite web |date=6 January 2011 |title=Research space stations arrive on Isle of Man |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-isle-of-man-12128590 |access-date=12 September 2011 |website=BBC News |archive-date=20 July 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720041420/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-isle-of-man-12128590 |url-status=live }}</ref>。

=== 電力供應 ===
馬恩島的電力供應由{{tsl|en|Manx Utilities Authority|馬恩島公用事業管理局}}負責。馬恩島通過40[[兆瓦|兆瓦]]的[[交流電|交流電]]鏈路（{{tsl|en|Isle of Man to England Interconnector|馬恩島到英格蘭互連器}}）連接到{{tsl|en|National Grid (Great Britain)|英國的國家電網}}。還有水力發電、天然氣和柴油發電機。政府還規劃了一個700兆瓦的海上風電場，大約是{{tsl|en|Walney Wind Farm|沃爾尼風電場}}的一半<ref name="4coff">{{cite web |date=1 February 2017 |title=Isle of Man Offshore Wind Farm |url=https://www.4coffshore.com/windfarms/windfarms.aspx?windfarmid=IM01 |access-date=14 November 2018 |website=4C Offshore |archive-date=15 September 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915122234/https://www.4coffshore.com/windfarms/windfarms.aspx?windfarmid=IM01 |url-status=live }}</ref>。

=== 供氣 ===
自1836年以來，馬恩島的用戶就開始使用用於照明和取暖的氣體，首先是作為[[煤氣|城市燃氣]]，然後是[[液化石油氣|液化石油氣]](LPG)；自2003年以來，[[天然氣|天然氣]]已經可用。正在研究[[氫經濟|氫]]作為補充或替代燃料的未來用途<ref>{{cite web|title=Impact report Appendix 19|url=https://www.gov.im/media/1368072/appendix-19-gas-grid.pdf|access-date=29 January 2022|website=www.gov.im}}</ref>。

=== 大麻種植 ===
2021年6月，禁止在馬恩島商業種植[[大麻_(植物)|大麻]]的法律被廢除，曼恩政府首次提供生產和出口大麻的許可證。2022年2月，曼恩居民和當地億萬富翁{{tsl|en|John Whittaker (businessman)|約翰·惠特克 (商人)|約翰·惠特克}}通過他的公司{{tsl|en|The Peel Group|皮爾NRE}}提議斥資1.36億美元用於建造大麻種植暖房和研究設施，並發展業務。宣布已為該設施的開發授予分區許可證。儘管在英國本土，[[醫用大麻|醫用大麻]]的供應受到嚴格限制，但海峽群島的澤西島和根西島一直在努力發展大麻產業<ref>{{cite web |url=https://hightimes.com/news/isle-of-man-plans-136-million-facility-off-coast-of-u-k/ |title=Isle Of Man Plans $136 Million Facility Off Coast of U.K. |publisher=High Times |date=2022-02-21 |accessdate=2022-02-26 |archive-date=2022-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220609225851/https://hightimes.com/news/isle-of-man-plans-136-million-facility-off-coast-of-u-k/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-isle-of-man-60404400 |title=Plans outlined for £100m Isle of Man medicinal cannabis complex |work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |date=16 February 2022 |accessdate=2022-02-26 |archive-date=2022-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220610064914/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-isle-of-man-60404400 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url = https://www.cnbc.com/2022/02/28/billionaire-john-whitaker-hopes-to-set-up-cannabis-farm-on-isle-of-man.html|title = Property billionaire hopes to set up huge cannabis farm on a tiny island in the Irish Sea|website = [[CNBC|CNBC]]|date = 28 February 2022|access-date = 2022-04-17|archive-date = 2022-05-01|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220501094828/https://www.cnbc.com/2022/02/28/billionaire-john-whitaker-hopes-to-set-up-cannabis-farm-on-isle-of-man.html}}</ref>。

== 文化 ==
{{tsl|en|Manx people|馬恩島人}}是一個[[凱爾特地區|凱爾特民族]]<ref>{{Cite book |last=Minahan |first=James |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=NwvoM-ZFoAgC |title=One Europe, Many Nations: A Historical Dictionary of European National Groups |date=31 January 2000 |publisher=Greenwood Publishing Group |isbn=9780313309847 |via=Google Books |access-date=7 May 2020 |archive-date=21 March 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150321014815/http://books.google.com/books?id=NwvoM-ZFoAgC |url-status=live }}</ref>。

馬恩島的文化經常被宣傳為受到其[[凱爾特人|凱爾特人]]的影響，在較小程度上受到其[[諾斯人|北歐]]起源的影響。靠近英國，在維多利亞時代作為英國旅遊目的地的受歡迎程度，以及來自英國的移民都意味著英國的文化至少從{{tsl|en|Revestment (Isle of Man)|馬恩島回歸|回歸}}開始就具有影響力。經過長期的[[盎格魯化|盎格魯化]]後，復興運動試圖保留倖存的馬恩島文化遺跡，人們對馬恩島語言、歷史和音樂傳統的興趣顯著增加。

=== 語言 ===
{{main|馬恩島語}}
[[File:Douglas_Isle_of_Man_welcome_sign.jpg|thumb]]和英語為特色]]

馬恩島的官方語言是[[英語|英語]]。傳統上講[[馬恩島語|馬恩島語]]，但據說“極度瀕危”<ref name="ManxUNESCO">{{cite web |date=19 August 2009 |title=UNESCO accepts Manx language is not 'extinct' |url=http://www.gov.im/lib/news/cso/unescoacceptsman.xml |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110511200853/http://www.gov.im/lib/news/cso/unescoacceptsman.xml |archive-date=11 May 2011 |access-date=20 August 2009 |publisher=Isle of Man Government}}</ref>。然而，它現在有越來越多的年輕演講者。

馬恩島語是一種[[蓋爾語|蓋爾語]]，是在不列顛群島使用的多種[[海島凱爾特語支|海島凱爾特語支]]之一<ref>{{cite web |last=Carpenter |first=Rachel N. |date=2011 |title=Mind Your P's and Q's: Revisiting the Insular Celtic hypothesis through working towards an original phonetic reconstruction of Insular Celtic |url=http://www.swarthmore.edu/SocSci/Linguistics/2011thesis/PDFs/CarpenterBMC.pdf |access-date=17 September 2011 |archive-date=14 October 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111014050617/http://www.swarthmore.edu/SocSci/Linguistics/2011thesis/PDFs/CarpenterBMC.pdf |url-status=live }}</ref>。根據英國於2001年3月27日代表馬恩島政府批准的《[[歐洲區域或少數民族語言憲章|歐洲區域或少數民族語言憲章]]》，馬恩島語已被正式承認為合法的{{tsl|en|autochthonous language|本土語言|本土}}[[地區語言|地區語言]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Kelly |first=Phil |title=Manx today by Phil Kelly |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/voices/multilingual/manx.shtml |access-date=17 September 2011 |website=BBC News |archive-date=11 August 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110811163952/http://www.bbc.co.uk/voices/multilingual/manx.shtml |url-status=live }}</ref>。

馬恩島語與[[愛爾蘭語|愛爾蘭語]]和[[蘇格蘭蓋爾語|蘇格蘭蓋爾語]]密切相關，但在正字法上是[[自成一類|自成一類]]的。

在島上，經常可以聽到[[馬恩島語|馬恩島語]]的問候{{lang|gv|moghrey mie}}（早上好）和{{lang|gv|fastyr mie}}（下午好）<ref>{{Cite book |last=Davies |first=Alan |title=An Introduction to Applied Linguistics |date=2007 |publisher=Edinburgh University Press |isbn=978-0-7486-3354-8 |edition=2nd The Manx}}</ref>。正如在愛爾蘭語和蘇格蘭蓋爾語中一樣，“晚上”和“下午”的概念用一個詞來表示<ref>{{cite web |title=Manx Culture |url=http://www.visitisleofman.com/culture/ |access-date=17 September 2011 |website=VisitIsleOfMan.com |archive-date=29 March 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120329103039/http://www.visitisleofman.com/culture/ |url-status=live }}</ref>。經常聽到的另外兩個馬恩島語表達方式是{{lang|gv|Gura mie eu}}（“謝謝”；熟悉的第二人稱單數形式{{lang|gv|Gura mie ayd}}）和{{lang|gv|traa dy liooar}}，意思是“足夠的時間”，代表了馬恩島人對生活態度的刻板看法<ref>{{Cite book |last=Arthur William |first=Moore |title=The Folk-Lore of the Isle of Man |date=1971 |publisher=Forgotten Books |isbn=1-60506-183-2 |edition=Reprint |page=274}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |date=8 January 2011 |title=Moscow Manx cheese |url=http://www.iomtoday.co.im/news/education/moscow_manx_cheese_1_2908142?showResult=true&pollContentId=7.52601 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120804201941/http://www.iomtoday.co.im/news/education/moscow_manx_cheese_1_2908142?showResult=true&pollContentId=7.52601 |archive-date=4 August 2012 |access-date=17 September 2011 |website=IOMToday}}</ref>。

2001年9月，[[曼島語小學|曼島語小學]]正式成立，截至2011年是世界唯一一所完全以曼島語授課的學校<ref>{{Citation | last=Skeealyn Vannin | year=2006年 | title=A Miscellany on the History, Culture and Language of the Isle of Man | volume=第7冊 | issue=第2期 | publisher=Journal of the Genealogical Society of Ireland | url=http://www.familyhistory.ie/docs/SKEEALYN%20VANNIN%20STORIES%20OF%20MANN.pdf | accessdate=2014年2月2日 | language=en | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070808025250/http://www.familyhistory.ie/docs/SKEEALYN%20VANNIN%20STORIES%20OF%20MANN.pdf | archivedate=2007年8月8日}}</ref>

在2011年馬恩島人口普查中，大約1,800名居民可以讀、寫和說馬恩島語<ref name="census-2011">{{cite web |title=Isle of Man Census Report 2011 |url=https://www.gov.im/media/207882/census2011reportfinalresized_1_.pdf |access-date=19 July 2019 |website=Gov.im |archive-date=6 June 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200606130246/https://www.gov.im/media/207882/census2011reportfinalresized_1_.pdf |url-status=live }}</ref>。

=== 符號 ===
{{main|三曲腿圖}}
[[File:The_Legs_of_Man_-_Isle_of_Man_Triskelion_-_kingsley_-_19-APR-09.jpg|right]]雕塑]]

幾個世紀以來，該島的標誌一直是所謂的“曼恩三足”（{{lang-gv|Tree Cassyn Vannin}}），即三條腿在大腿處相連的[[三曲腿圖|三曲腿圖]]。馬恩島三曲腿圖的歷史可以肯定地追溯到13世紀後期，其起源不確定。有人認為它的起源位於[[西西里島|西西里島]]，這個島嶼自古以來就與三曲腿圖聯繫在一起<ref>{{Cite book |title=Archeologia del Mediterraneo: Studi in onore di Ernesto De Miro |date=2003 |publisher=L'Erma di Bretschneider |isbn=978-88-8265-134-3 |editor-last=Fiorentini |editor-first=Graziella |pages=735–736 |editor-last2=De Miro |editor-first2=Ernesto |editor-last3=Calderone |editor-first3=Anna |editor-last4=Caccamo Caltabiano |editor-first4=Maria}}|date=December 2017}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal |last=Wilson |first=RJA |date=2000 |title=On the Trail of the Triskeles: From the McDonald Institute to Archaic Greek Sicily |journal=[[Cambridge_Archaeological_Journal|Cambridge Archaeological Journal]] |volume=10 |issue=1 |pages=35–61 |doi=10.1017/S0959774300000020 |s2cid=162858347}}</ref>。

該符號出現在該島的[[曼島旗幟|官方旗幟]]和[[曼島徽章|官方徽章]]以及[[曼島鎊|其貨幣]]中。馬恩島三曲腿圖可能反映在島上的座右銘「''{{lang|la|Quocunque jeceris stabit}}''」中，該座右銘作為該島國徽的一部分出現。拉丁格言翻譯為“無論你扔什麼，它都會站立”<ref name="kinvig-9192" />或“無論你扔到哪裡，它都會站立”<ref name="govmotto">{{cite web |title=Island Facts |url=http://www.gov.im/categories/business-and-industries/iom-key-facts-guide/island-facts/ |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304050532/https://www.gov.im/categories/business-and-industries/iom-key-facts-guide/island-facts/ |archive-date=4 March 2016 |access-date=15 January 2016 |website=Gov.im |publisher=Public Services, Isle of Man Government}}</ref>。它可以追溯到 17 世紀後期，當時已知它出現在島上的鑄幣上<ref name="kinvig-9192">{{Cite book |last=Kinvig |first=R.H. |title=The Isle of Man: A social, cultural and political history |url=https://archive.org/details/isleofmansocialc0000kinv |date=1975 |publisher=Charles E. Tuttle |isbn=0-8048-1165-2 |location=Rutland, Vermont |pages=[https://archive.org/details/isleofmansocialc0000kinv/page/91 91]–92}}</ref>。也有人提出，這句座右銘最初是指當時普遍存在的劣質造幣——如“無論經過怎樣的測試，它都會通過”<ref name="manxnotebook-legs">{{cite web |title=The Three Legs of Man |url=http://www.isle-of-man.com/manxnotebook/history/legs.htm |access-date=15 September 2011 |website=Isle-of-Man.com) |archive-date=11 June 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110611134019/http://www.isle-of-man.com/manxnotebook/history/legs.htm |url-status=live }}. This webpage cited: {{Cite journal |last=Wagner |first=A. R. |title=The Origin of the Arms of Man |date=1959–1960 |volume=6 |journal=Manx Museum}}. This webpage also cited: {{Cite journal |last=Megaw |first=B. R. S. |title=The Ship Seals of the Kings of Man |date=1959–1960 |volume=6 |journal=Manx Museum}}|date=December 2017}}</ref>。

[[豚草|豚草]]或[[新疆千里光|新疆千里光]]被稱為馬恩島的[[國花|國花]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gov.im/media/402197/cushag_code_july_2013.pdf |title=The Cushag Code: A code of best practice for the management of common ragwort Senecio jacobaea |publisher=Isle of Man Government |date=July 2013 |access-date=15 July 2021 |url-status=live |archive-date=15 April 2021 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415095824/https://www.gov.im/media/402197/cushag_code_july_2013.pdf }}</ref>。

=== 宗教 ===
{{See also|聖公會索多暨馬恩教區}}
[[File:Peel_Cathedral_01.JPG|thumb]]]]

島上主要的宗教傳統是[[基督教|基督教]]。在新教改革之前，該島作為統一[[天主教會|天主教會]]的一部分有著悠久的歷史，在宗教改革之後的幾年裡，島上的宗教當局，以及後來的島上居民，都接受了英國君主制的宗教權威和[[英格蘭教會|英格蘭教會]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Moore |first=A. |title=Diocesan Histories. Sodor and Mann. |url=http://www.isle-of-man.com/manxnotebook/fulltext/dh1893/index.htm |access-date=24 February 2009 |archive-date=10 April 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180410123532/http://www.isle-of-man.com/manxnotebook/fulltext/dh1893/index.htm |url-status=live }}</ref>。它也受到愛爾蘭宗教傳統的影響。該島形成了一個名為[[聖公會索多暨馬恩教區|索多暨馬恩]]的獨立教區，在遙遠的過去包括中世紀的曼王國和蘇格蘭群島（古諾爾斯語中的“Suðreyjar”）。它現在由16個堂區組成，<ref>{{cite web |last=Gumbley |first=Ken |date=1 March 2012 |title=Diocese of Sodor and Man |url=http://www.gumbley.net/diocese.htm |access-date=15 August 2019 |website=Welcome to Kirk Braddan |archive-date=14 June 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170614124455/http://www.gumbley.net/diocese.htm |url-status=live }}</ref>自1541年<ref>Act of Parliament (1541) 33 Hen.8 c.31</ref>已成為[[約克教省|約克教省]]的一部分<ref>{{cite web |date=28 May 2012 |title=England-Sodor & Man |url=http://www.anglicancommunion.org/tour/diocese.cfm?Idind=214 |url-status=unfit |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120528223800/http://www.anglicancommunion.org/tour/diocese.cfm?Idind=214 |archive-date=28 May 2012 |access-date=15 August 2019 |website=Anglican Communion}}</ref>。（這些現代教會堂區與本文“地方政府”下提到的島上古代堂區並不對應，而是更接近地反映了當前人口的地理分佈。）

其他基督教教堂也在馬恩島運作。第二大教派是[[英國循道會|衛理公會]]，其馬恩島區的人數接近英國國教教區。有八個天主教教區教堂，包括在[[天主教利物浦總教區|天主教利物浦總教區]]<ref>{{cite web |title=The Archdiocese of Liverpool |url=http://www.liverpoolcatholic.org.uk |access-date=15 August 2019 |website=Liverpool Catholic |archive-date=25 October 2021 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211025120855/http://liverpoolcatholic.org.uk/ |url-status=live }}</ref>，以及[[東正教|東正教]]基督徒的存在。此外，還有五個[[浸信會|浸信會]]教堂、四個[[五旬節|五旬節]]教會、[[救世軍|救世軍]]、[[耶穌基督後期聖徒教會|耶穌基督後期聖徒教會]]的一個{{tsl|en|The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints in the Isle of Man|支會}}、兩個[[耶和華見證人|耶和華見證人]]會眾、兩個[[聯合歸正教會|聯合歸正教會]]教堂，以及其他基督教教堂。有一個小[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]社區，在道格拉斯有自己的清真寺，還有一個小[[猶太|猶太]]社區；查看{{tsl|en|History of the Jews in the Isle of Man|馬恩島猶太人的歷史}}<ref>{{cite web |date=28 May 2012 |title=Religious Faiths and Organisations |url=http://www.gov.im/IsleOfMan/religion.xml |url-status=unfit |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030608055741/http://www.gov.im/IsleOfMan/religion.xml |archive-date=8 June 2003 |access-date=15 August 2019 |website=Isle of Man Government}}</ref>。

=== 神話、傳說和民間傳說 ===
[[File:Isle_of_Man_Peel_Castle.jpg|right]]]]
在馬恩島神話中，該島由海神{{tsl|en|Manannán mac Lir|Manannán}}統治，他將他的薄霧籠罩在島嶼周圍以保護它免受入侵者的侵害。關於曼恩這個名字的起源的主要民間理論之一是它是以Manannán命名的。

在馬恩島的[[民俗|民俗]]傳統中，有許多關於神話生物和人物的故事。其中包括''{{tsl|en|Buggane}}''，一種{{tsl|en|Malevolent spirit|惡毒的靈魂}}，據傳說，它一怒之下炸毀了聖特里尼安教堂的屋頂；''{{tsl|en|Fenodyree}}''；''{{tsl|en|Glashtyn}}''；還有''{{tsl|en|Moddey Dhoo}}''，一隻[[黑犬|幽靈般的黑犬]]，在[[皮爾城堡|皮爾城堡]]的牆壁和走廊裡游盪。

據說馬恩島也是{{tsl|en|Mooinjer veggey|Mooinjer veggey|仙女}}的家園，在當地被稱為“小人物”或“他們自己”。有一座很有名的{{tsl|en|Fairy Bridge (Isle of Man)|仙女橋}}，據說如果經過它時沒有向仙女們說早安或午安，那是不吉利的。過去，在橋上留下一枚硬幣以確保好運是一種傳統。其他類型的仙女是''Mi'raj''和''{{tsl|en|Arkan Sonney}}''。

一個古老的愛爾蘭故事講述了當愛爾蘭傳奇巨人{{tsl|en|Fionn mac Cumhaill}}（通常被稱為 Finn McCool）撕毀一部分土地並將其扔給蘇格蘭競爭對手時，[[內湖_(英國)|內湖]]是如何形成的。他失手了，大片的土地降落在[[愛爾蘭海|愛爾蘭海]]，從而創造了這個島。

皮爾城堡被提出作為亞瑟王[[阿瓦隆|阿瓦隆]]的可能位置<ref>{{cite web |title=Avalon's Location |url=http://www.electricscotland.com/history/avalon.htm |access-date=28 February 2015 |website=Electricscotland.com |archive-date=23 March 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150323023956/http://www.electricscotland.com/history/avalon.htm |url-status=live }}</ref>或作為聖杯城堡的位置，[[蘭斯洛特|蘭斯洛特]]與{{tsl|en|Fairy Bridge (Isle of Man)|梅里亞岡特}}國王在劍橋相遇的地點<ref>King Arthur, Norma Lorre Goodrich, Harper and Row, 1989, p. 318</ref>。

最常被重複的神話之一是，被判犯有巫術罪的人會在桶裡滾下聖莊斯附近的一座小山Slieau Whallian。然而，這是一個源自蘇格蘭傳奇的19世紀傳奇，而蘇格蘭傳奇又源自一個德國傳奇。另外，1951年在卡斯爾敦的女巫磨坊開設了一個巫術博物館。那個地方實際上從未有過女巫聚會。神話只是隨著博物館的開放而產生的<ref>{{cite web |title=Manx witchcraft and sorcery probed by academic - Isle of Man Today |url=http://www.iomtoday.co.im/news/isle-of-man-news/manx-witchcraft-and-sorcery-probed-by-academic-1-1744837 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151227154121/http://www.iomtoday.co.im/news/isle-of-man-news/manx-witchcraft-and-sorcery-probed-by-academic-1-1744837 |archive-date=27 December 2015 |access-date=10 November 2017 |website=Iomtoday.co.im}}</ref>。然而，草藥學和使用護身符來預防和治療人和動物的疾病和疾病有著悠久的傳統<ref>{{Cite book |last1=Nisbet |first1=Robert A |title=Yn Lioar Manninagh: The Journal of the Isle of Man Natural History and Antiquarian Society |last2=Rhys |first2=John |date=1897 |publisher=Brown & Sons |volume=3 |location=Douglas |pages=303–314 |language=en |chapter=Folk-Medicine in the Isle of Man – A. W. Moore, M. A. |oclc=1110392917 |chapter-url=http://www.isle-of-man.com/manxnotebook/iomnhas/lm3p303.htm |access-date=20 June 2019 |archive-date=25 February 2021 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225083154/http://www.isle-of-man.com/manxnotebook/iomnhas/lm3p303.htm |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |last1=Chiverrell |first1=R. |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=yjHHVG_aiOAC&pg=PA353 |title=A New History of the Isle of Man: The modern period 1830-1999 |last2=Belchem |first2=J. |last3=Thomas |first3=G. |last4=Duffy |first4=S. |last5=Mytum |first5=H. |publisher=Liverpool University Press |year=2000 |isbn=978-0-85323-726-6 |series=A New History of the Isle of Man |page=353 |access-date=15 August 2019 |archive-date=3 August 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803113305/https://books.google.com/books?id=yjHHVG_aiOAC&pg=PA353 |url-status=live }}</ref>。

=== 音樂 ===
[[File:Bee_Gees_Plaque_-_Union_Mills_IOM_-_kingsley_-_21-APR-09.jpg|right]]牌匾]]
馬恩島的音樂反映了[[凱爾特人|凱爾特]]、北歐和其他影響，包括來自其鄰國[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]、[[愛爾蘭島|愛爾蘭]]、[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]和[[威爾斯|威爾斯]]。島上有各種各樣的音樂，如搖滾、藍調、爵士和流行音樂。

自1970年代以來，其傳統民間音樂經歷了復興，從[[拉姆齊_(曼島)|拉姆齊]]的一個名為{{tsl|en|Yn Chruinnaght}}的音樂節開始<ref>{{cite web |title=Trad music in the Isle of Man |url=http://www.ceolas.org/Regions/Manx-article.html |access-date=28 February 2015 |website=Ceolas.org |archive-date=13 April 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150413002917/http://www.ceolas.org/Regions/Manx-article.html |url-status=live }}</ref>。這是在1974年最後一位以馬恩島語為母語的人去世後，馬恩島語言和文化普遍復興的一部分。

馬恩島在[[誰人樂團|誰人樂團]]歌曲《{{tsl|en|Happy Jack (song)|快樂傑克}}》中被提及為歌曲主角的故鄉，無論發生什麼事，他總是處於狂喜的狀態。{{tsl|en|Christy Moore|克里斯·蒂摩爾}}的歌曲《The Craic was 90 in the Isle of Man》描述了該島旅遊業全盛時期的一次熱鬧的訪-{}-問。該島也是[[比知樂隊|比知樂隊]]的莫禮斯、羅賓和巴利·傑布的出生地；三人組的銅像於2021年7月在道格拉斯長廊上揭幕<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-isle-of-man-57769115 |title=Isle of Man Bee Gees statue unveiled on Douglas seafront |work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |date= 8 July 2021|access-date=2022-02-20 |archive-date=31 January 2022 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220131123745/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-isle-of-man-57769115 |url-status=live }}</ref>。

=== 食物 ===
過去，島上的基本國菜是''土豆和鯡魚''、煮土豆和鯡魚。這道樸素的菜餚得到了島上自給自足的農民的支持，幾個世紀以來，他們在土地上{{tsl|en|Crofting|小農耕作}}並在大海中捕魚。薯條、奶酪和肉汁，一種類似於[[芝士淋肉汁薯條|芝士淋肉汁薯條]]的菜餚，在島上的大多數快餐店都有，由厚切[[薯條|薯條]]組成，上面覆蓋著[[車打芝士|車打芝士]]絲，上面放著濃稠的肉汁<ref>{{cite web |last=isleofman.com |title=Attractions :: isleofman.com |url=http://www.isleofman.com/attractions/cuisine/ |access-date=10 November 2017 |website=Isleofman.com |archive-date=26 December 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171226050135/http://www.isleofman.com/attractions/cuisine |url-status=live }}</ref>。 然而，截至2018年馬恩島美食節，[[女王扇貝|女王扇貝]]已成為馬恩島的國菜<ref>{{cite web |title=National Dish of the Isle of Man - Locate Isle of Man |url=https://www.locate.im/articles/national-dish-of-the-isle-of-man- |access-date=20 May 2020 |website=www.locate.im |archive-date=24 August 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200824083028/https://www.locate.im/articles/national-dish-of-the-isle-of-man- |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Queenies crowned Isle of Man's national dish |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-isle-of-man-45547406 |website=BBC News |date=17 September 2018 |access-date=2022-05-05 |archive-date=2022-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220615023410/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-isle-of-man-45547406 }}</ref>。

傳統上，海鮮在當地飲食中佔很大比例。儘管近年來商業捕魚有所下降，但當地美食包括馬恩島[[醃魚_(英國)|醃魚]]（煙熏鯡魚），它們是由該島西海岸皮爾的煙熏廠生產的，儘管這些日子主要來自[[北海_(大西洋)|北海]]鯡魚<ref name="Assoc1971">{{Cite journal |date=November 1971 |title=American Motorcyclist |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ffYDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA22 |journal=American Motorcyclist : The Monthly Journal of the American Motorcyclist Association |publisher=American Motorcyclist Association |page=22 |issn=0277-9358 |access-date=12 September 2011 |archive-date=9 May 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130509180417/http://books.google.com/books?id=ffYDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA22 |url-status=live }}</ref>。煙熏廠還生產其他特色菜，包括熏鮭魚和培根。

螃蟹、龍蝦和扇貝是商業捕撈的，而[[女王扇貝|女王扇貝]]（''queenies''）被認為是一種特殊的美味，味道清淡、甜美<ref>{{cite web |last=Evans |first=Ann |date=30 May 2009 |title=Scallops the main ingredient of unique gathering for foodies; SUN, sea, sand and shellfish |url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Scallops+the+main+ingredient+of+unique+gathering+for+foodies%3B+SUN,...-a0200817093 |access-date=12 September 2011 |website=Coventry Evening Telegraph |publisher=Coventry Newspapers |via=TheFreeLibrary.com |archive-date=25 October 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025021554/http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Scallops+the+main+ingredient+of+unique+gathering+for+foodies%3B+SUN,...-a0200817093 |url-status=live }}</ref>。鱈魚、[[魣鱈|魣鱈]]和鯖魚通常以角度擺放在餐桌上，淡水鱒魚和鮭魚可以從當地的河流和湖泊中獲取，由東海岸科爾納的政府魚類孵化場提供支持。

牛、羊、豬和家禽都是商業養殖的；來自山區農場的馬恩島羊肉是一道受歡迎的菜餚。{{tsl|en|Manx Loaghtan|洛夫坦}}是馬恩島綿羊的本土品種，其肉質肥厚，深受廚師青睞<ref>{{cite web |last=Kallaway |first=Jane |title=Award winning organic lamb |url=http://www.langleychase.co.uk/ |access-date=12 September 2011 |publisher=Langley Chase Organic Farm |archive-date=4 September 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110904024332/http://www.langleychase.co.uk/ |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Purely Isle of Man |url=http://www.gov.im/lib/docs/iomfinance/factsheets/isleofmanproduce.pdf |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012054640/http://www.gov.im/lib/docs/iomfinance/factsheets/isleofmanproduce.pdf |archive-date=12 October 2012 |access-date=12 September 2011 |publisher=Isle of Man Department of Finance}}</ref>，出現在BBC的''{{tsl|en|MasterChef (British TV series)|我要做廚神 (英國節目)|我要做廚神}}''系列菜餚中。

馬恩島芝士也取得了一些成功，以煙熏和香草味品種為特色，並在英國的許多連鎖超市都有庫存<ref>{{cite web |date=2010 |title=Isle of Man Oak Smoked Mature Cheddar Wins Bronze Medal at The British Cheese Awards 2010 |url=http://isleofman.isle-news.com/archives/isle-of-man-oak-smoked-mature-cheddar-wins-bronze-medal-at-the-british-cheese-awards-2010/6768/ |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120325175544/http://isleofman.isle-news.com/archives/isle-of-man-oak-smoked-mature-cheddar-wins-bronze-medal-at-the-british-cheese-awards-2010/6768/ |archive-date=25 March 2012 |access-date=12 September 2011 |website=Isle News}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |date=15 October 2003 |title=Bumper Sales for Manx Cheese |url=http://www.iomtoday.co.im/news/isle-of-man-news/bumper_sales_for_manx_cheese_1_1750532 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120803063502/http://www.iomtoday.co.im/news/isle-of-man-news/bumper_sales_for_manx_cheese_1_1750532 |archive-date=3 August 2012 |access-date=12 September 2011 |website=IOMToday}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |date=22 March 2007 |title=Success at World Cheese Awards |url=http://www.isleofman.com/News/article.aspx?article=5017 |access-date=12 September 2011 |website=IsleOfMan.com |archive-date=22 March 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120322062013/http://www.isleofman.com/News/article.aspx?article=5017 |url-status=live }}</ref>。馬恩島芝士在2005年英國芝士獎中獲得銅牌，全年銷量為578噸。馬恩島車打芝士已出口到加拿大，在一些超市有售<ref>{{cite web |title=PC Black Label English Isle of Man Extra Old Cheddar Cheese |url=http://www.provigo.ca/en_CA/products/productlisting/pc-black-label-isle-of-man-extra-old-cheddar-cheese-aged-14-mont0.html |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161118035745/http://www.provigo.ca/en_CA/products/productlisting/pc-black-label-isle-of-man-extra-old-cheddar-cheese-aged-14-mont0.html |archive-date=18 November 2016 |access-date=17 November 2016 |website=Provigo}}</ref>。

啤酒由成立於1850年的{{tsl|en|Okells Brewery|奧克爾啤酒廠}}以商業規模釀造，是島上最大的啤酒廠；還有{{tsl|en|Bushy's Brewery|布殊啤酒廠}}和連帽公羊啤酒廠。類似於[[德國|德國]][[啤酒純釀法|啤酒純釀法]]的1874年馬恩島純啤酒法案仍然有效：根據該法案，啤酒釀造商只能在啤酒中使用水、麥芽、糖和啤酒花<ref>{{cite web |title=Purely Isle of Man |url=http://www.gov.im/lib/docs/iomfinance/factsheets/isleofmanproduce.pdf |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130430164916/http://www.gov.im/lib/docs/iomfinance/factsheets/isleofmanproduce.pdf |archive-date=30 April 2013 |access-date=10 June 2015 |website=Gov.im |publisher=Isle of Man Government}}</ref>。

=== 運動 ===
馬恩島作為一個國家參加[[英聯邦運動會|英聯邦運動會]]和[[島嶼運動會|島嶼運動會]]，並於2011年舉辦了第四屆[[英聯邦青年運動會|英聯邦青年運動會]]。馬恩島的運動員在英聯邦運動會上贏得了{{tsl|en|Isle of Man at the Commonwealth Games|三枚金牌}}，其中包括2006年自行車運動員[[馬克·卡文迪什|馬克·卡文迪什]]在{{tsl|en|Scratch race|集體爭先賽}}。{{tsl|en|International Island Games Association|國際海島運動協會|島嶼運動會}}於1985年首次在島上舉行，並於2001年再次舉行。2019年，{{tsl|en|F.C. Isle of Man|FC馬恩島}}成立，是一支[[英格蘭西北郡足球聯賽|西北郡聯賽]]球隊。
[[File:The_National_Sports_Centre_(geograph_3710042).jpg|thumb]]
馬恩島的球隊和個人在島上和島外參加許多運動，包括[[橄欖球|橄欖球]]、[[足球|足球]]、[[體操|體操]]、[[草地曲棍球|草地曲棍球]]、[[籃網球|籃網球]]、[[跆拳道|跆拳道]]、[[保齡球_(廣義)|保齡球]]、障礙賽和[[板球|板球]]。馬恩島足球俱樂部將在下一場聯賽中參加[[西北郡足球聯賽|西北郡足球聯賽]]<ref>{{cite web |title=FC Isle of Man promoted after historic play-off final victory |url=https://www.manxradio.com/news/isle-of-man-sport/fc-isle-of-man-promoted-after-historic-play-off-final-victory/ |website=Manx Radio |language=en |access-date=2022-05-05 |archive-date=2022-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220619022827/https://www.manxradio.com/news/isle-of-man-sport/fc-isle-of-man-promoted-after-historic-play-off-final-victory/ }}</ref>。它是一個島嶼，許多類型的水上運動也受到居民的歡迎。

==== 電單車比賽 ====
{{details|曼島TT賽}}
與該島相關的主要國際賽事是[[曼島TT賽|馬恩島旅遊獎盃賽]]，俗稱“TT”<ref>Wright, David. 100 Years of the Isle of Man TT: A Century of Motorcycle Racing. The Crowood Press, 2007</ref>，始於{{tsl|en|1907 Isle of Man TT|1907年曼島TT賽|1907年}}。它發生在五月下旬和六月上旬。TT現在是一項國際性的電單車公路賽事，曾經是世界錦標賽的一部分，長期以來被認為是“世界上最偉大電單車運動賽事”之一<ref>Disko, Sasha. The Image of the "Tourist Trophy" and British Motorcycling in the Weimar Republic. International Journal of Motorcycle Studies, Nov 2007</ref>。在為期兩週的時間內，它已成為電單車文化的節日，為島上的經濟做出了巨大貢獻，並已成為馬恩島人身份的一部分<ref>Vaukins, Simon. The Isle of Man TT Races: Politics, Economics and National Identity. International Journal of Motorcycle Studies, Nov 2007</ref>。對許多人來說，小島擁有“世界公路賽車之都”的稱號<ref>Faragher, Martin. "Cultural History: Motor-Cycle Road Racing." A New History of the Isle of Man Volume V: The Modern Period 1830–1999. Ed. John Belchem. Liverpool: Liverpool University Press, 2000</ref>。

{{tsl|en|Manx Grand Prix|馬恩島大獎賽}}是一項針對業餘愛好者和私人參賽者的獨立電單車賽事，在8月下旬和9月初使用相同的{{convert|60.70|km|mi|abbr=on}}<ref>{{cite web |date=2009 |title=2009 Manx Grand Prix Supplementary Regulations |url=http://www.manxgrandprix.org/Competitors/MGP%20regulations%2009.pdf |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120310131221/http://www.manxgrandprix.org/Competitors/MGP%20regulations%2009.pdf |archive-date=10 March 2012 |access-date=15 August 2019 |website=manxgrandprix.org |page=4}}</ref>{{tsl|en|Snaefell Mountain Course|斯奈菲爾山賽道}}。

在1990年代，[[世嘉|世嘉]]發布了一款名為{{tsl|en|Manx TT Superbike|曼島TT賽超級電單車}}的街機遊戲，基於電單車比賽<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC3mTMFw64OfhUfO8Y0G7Ocw/ |title=Leo the Tiger |publisher=YouTube |date= |accessdate=2022-02-20 |archive-date=5 February 2022 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220205223320/https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC3mTMFw64OfhUfO8Y0G7Ocw/ |url-status=live }}</ref>。

==== 卡馬格 ====
在19世紀引入足球之前，{{tsl|en|Cammag|Cammag|卡馬格}}是島上的傳統運動<ref>{{cite web |title=The Game of Cammag |url=http://www.celticlife.ca/index.php/Sports/the-game-of-cammag.html |access-date=12 September 2011 |website=Celticlife.ca |archive-date=29 October 2021 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211029012448/http://celticlife.com/ |url-status=live }}</ref>。它類似於愛爾蘭的[[板棍球|板棍球]]和蘇格蘭的{{tsl|en|Shinty|簡化曲棍球}}遊戲。現在在{{tsl|en|St John's, Isle of Man|聖莊斯}}有一年一度的比賽。

=== 劇院和電影院 ===
建於1899年，由建築師{{tsl|en|Frank Matcham|弗蘭克·馬查姆}}設計<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.villagaiety.com/about-us/history/|title=History|website=www.villagaiety.com|access-date=2022-05-05|archive-date=2022-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220610062006/https://www.villagaiety.com/about-us/history/}}</ref>，並於1976年恢復到原來的輝煌，道格拉斯長廊上的政府擁有的{{tsl|en|Gaiety Theatre, Isle of Man|歡樂劇院和歌劇院}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.visitisleofman.com/experience/gaiety-theatre-p1293051|title=Gaiety Theatre - Visit Isle of Man|website=www.visitisleofman.com|access-date=2022-05-05|archive-date=2022-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220612072739/https://www.visitisleofman.com/experience/gaiety-theatre-p1293051}}</ref>每年都會舉辦戲劇、音樂劇、音樂會和喜劇表演-圓形的。在歡樂劇院大樓內，百老匯電影院可容納154人，並兼作會議場所<ref>{{Cite web |title=Broadway Cinema |url=http://www.gov.im/villagaiety/broadway.xml/ |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130306124729/http://www.gov.im/villagaiety/broadway.xml |archive-date=6 March 2013 |access-date=6 March 2013 |website=Gov.im}}</ref>。

王宮電影院位於廢棄的{{tsl|en|Castle Mona|莫娜城堡}}酒店旁邊，由塞夫頓集團經營。它有兩個屏幕：屏幕一可容納293名客戶，而屏幕二較小，容量僅為95人。它於2011年8月進行了大規模翻新<ref>{{Cite web |title=Cinemas Refurbishment |url=http://www.iomtoday.co.im/lifestyle/manx-entertainment-news/palace-cinema-reopens-1-3782747/ |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://archive.today/20130412224857/http://www.iomtoday.co.im/lifestyle/manx-entertainment-news/palace-cinema-reopens-1-3782747/ |archive-date=12 April 2013 |access-date=6 March 2013 |website=Iomtoday.co.im}}</ref>。

=== 動物群 ===
{{Main|馬恩島貓}}
[[File:Black_Manx_cat.JPG|黑色馬恩島貓]]
兩種家養動物與馬恩島有特​​別的聯繫，儘管它們也存在於其他地方。

[[馬恩島貓|馬恩島貓]]是一種貓，以其基因突變而聞名，導致它的尾巴變​​短。這條尾巴的長度可以從幾英寸（稱為“矮胖”）到完全不存在或“粗壯”。與大多數貓相比，馬恩島貓顯示出多種顏色，並且通常有更長的後腿。這些貓在硬幣和郵票上被用作馬恩島的象徵，有一次，馬恩島政府經營了一個繁殖中心，以確保該品種的延續<ref>{{Cite book |last=Commings |first=Karen |url=https://archive.org/details/manxcats00kare/page/7 |title=Manx Cats: Everything about Purchase, Care, Nutrition, Grooming, and Behavior |date=1999 |publisher=Barron's Educational |isbn=978-0764107535 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/manxcats00kare/page/7 7–10] |url-access=registration}}</ref>。
[[File:Manx_loaghtan.jpg|thumb]]
{{tsl|en|Manx Loaghtan|馬恩島洛夫坦}}羊是該島的本土品種。它有深棕色的羊毛和四個，有時是六個，角。肉被認為是美味佳餚<ref>{{Cite news |date=16 November 2009 |title=Farming the Manx Loaghtan sheep |language=en-GB |work=BBC News |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/local/isleofman/hi/people_and_places/nature/newsid_8333000/8333801.stm |access-date=15 August 2019 |archive-date=6 May 2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100506065202/http://news.bbc.co.uk/local/isleofman/hi/people_and_places/nature/newsid_8333000/8333801.stm |url-status=live }}</ref>。島上有幾隻羊群，英格蘭和[[澤西島|澤西島]]已經開始飼養其他羊群。

最近到達島上的是[[紅頸袋鼠|紅頸袋鼠]]，它現在是在逃離野生動物園後在島上建立的<ref>{{Cite news |date=14 August 2016 |title=Wallabies flourishing in the wild on Isle of Man |work=The Guardian |url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2016/aug/14/wallabies-isle-of-man-wild-australia |access-date=10 November 2017 |archive-date=8 November 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171108181734/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2016/aug/14/wallabies-isle-of-man-wild-australia |url-status=live }}</ref>。當地警方報告越來越多的袋鼠相關電話<ref>{{Cite news |last=Marshall |first=Francesca |date=7 September 2018 |title=Calls for wallaby warning signs to be implemented on the Isle of Man to tackle growing numbers |language=en-GB |work=The Telegraph |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2018/09/07/calls-wallaby-warning-signs-implemented-isle-man-tackle-growing/ |access-date=15 August 2019 |issn=0307-1235 |archive-date=9 September 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180909222009/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2018/09/07/calls-wallaby-warning-signs-implemented-isle-man-tackle-growing/ |url-status=live }}</ref>。

{{tsl|en|Garff|加夫}}也有許多野山羊，這是2018年1月在廷瓦爾德法院提出的問題<ref>Tynwald Hansard 16 January 2018, Question 9</ref>。

2016年3月，馬恩島成為第一個被納入聯合國教科文組織[[生物圈保護區|生物圈保護區]]網絡的整個領土<ref>{{Cite news |last=Morris |first=Hugh |title=Isle of Man awarded UNESCO status |work=The Daily Telegraph |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/destinations/europe/united-kingdom/england/isle-of-man/articles/isle-of-man-added-to-unesco-biosphere-reserve-list/ |access-date=28 June 2016 |archive-date=31 May 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160531184249/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/destinations/europe/united-kingdom/england/isle-of-man/articles/isle-of-man-added-to-unesco-biosphere-reserve-list/ |url-status=live }}</ref>。

